Umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus (COVID-19) wiyongereye cyane mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abanduye icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ko ibihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/mu Karere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza bifite ihame rimwe, ryemeza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda kihuta mu bihugu byose nubwo kiri mu byiciro bitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu.
Bitewe n'ubumenyi bufatika bwatanzwe n'Ubutaliyani, igihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bigomba kwitegura kugira ngo byihutire kwiyongera kw'abarwayi bazakenera ubuvuzi, cyane cyane mu buvuzi bwagutse.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, havumbuwe icyorezo cya Pneumonia cy'ubwoko butaramenyekana.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa SARS-CoV-2 (Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2).
Ni yo mpamvu uburwayi buterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 bwiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, amakuru yemewe ni uko 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara y'ubuhumekero, hamwe cyangwa idafite amapfupfa, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu 14% banduye, COVID-19 yatumye barwara cyane bigatuma barwara cyane bigatuma bajya mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% banduye barwaye cyane bigatuma bakenera kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4% gusa.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turimo dusuzuma uko ibintu byifashe mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza (UK) ku bijyanye n'ibyago bya COVID-19 kandi tubigereranya n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone turagereranya imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020 n'imibare iriho muri iki gihe mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Ubushinwa ni bwo bwakurikiye COVID-19 ikwirakwira cyane mu buryo bw'ibarurishamibare, kandi ubu ni bwo bufite imbaraga zo gukwirakwiza icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi.
Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Mu nomero yo ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020 ya EuroSurveillance, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere b'i Burayi bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 nk'uko byemejwe na WHO.
Mu karere ka EU/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye bagarutse bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, batangajwe n'u Bufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 yari imaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 30 bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza (UK), aho hari hamaze kuvugwa abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 bapfuye kuva ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hari hamaze kuvugwa abantu 17,750 banduye n'abantu 1,441.
Kubona imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye COVID-19 n'ubwirakabiri bwayo
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) gitanga amakuru y'ibyumweru bya COVID-19 bya buri gihugu ku isi yose, byungukiwe gusa n'abakozi ba Minisiteri z'Ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere, n'ibikoresho bya leta nka WHO, bigasubirwamo buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 igenda mu Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza no kuyigereranya n'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani.
Nk'impinduka y'ibimenyetso by'ibikorwa bya COVID-19, twabaze iminsi 14 y'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19, bityo dufata ingendo kamere ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza mu gihe cyo kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twerekanye kandi imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye muri buri gihugu kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, tugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Imyiteguro ya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Imyiteguro y'ibyumweru 14 byo kwiyongera kwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza muri rusange yakurikije iy'intara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma buzamuka cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho byuzuza).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'izamuka ryihuse ry'umubare w'abanduye muri Ubutaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byerekanye ubwiyongere nk'ubwo bw'ibyago by'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 (ibikoresho byuzuza).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza ingano y'Ubutaliyani n'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Ni ngombwa ko tumenya ko, kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibindi bihugu 15 bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza byari bimaze gutangaza umubare w'abanduye ugereranywa n'u Butaliyani mu byumweru 3 gusa bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza wiyongera cyane.
Imyiteguro igaragara mu byorezo bya COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo kiri kugenda mu buryo buhuriranye mu bihugu byose.
Ibi bibaye nubwo ibihugu biri mu byiciro bitandukanye, n'ubwo hari itandukaniro ry'ibisubizo by'ubuzima rusange by'igihugu, kandi ibihugu bifite ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo gutandukanya abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenyekane ko bafite COVID-19, harimo no gupima.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu duce twanduye mu Butaliyani basobanuye ko 10% by'abarwayi banduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'indembe byo muri utwo duce byamaze kugera ku bushobozi bwabyo.
Amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ubu aboneka ku rugero rwa EU/EEA ku bantu 6% na 1% gusa (amakuru ntabwo agaragazwa).
Ariko kandi, ibyo bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo bikomeze amakuru y'ubugenzuzi ahari, agaragaza imibare y'abanduye n'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 mu Budage, ku gipimo cy'ibitanda 4.2 ku 100,000 mu Bubiligi, bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini hagati yo kubona ibitanda byo mu bitaro byagutse n'ibyo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bw'inzitizi mu Burayi.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite amikoro make cyangwa menshi ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 byo mu bitaro byagutse n'ibyo mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bw'inzitizi ku bantu 100,000 mu 201011).
Mu gihe imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari mu bitaro muri buri gihugu cya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ibipimo byakozwe n'ubuvuzi bigaragaza ko hari ibyago byo kurenga 90% by'ibitanda by'indembe, nk'uko byatangajwe mu igenzura rya gatandatu ry'ingamba za ECDC ku bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko ibipimo by'ubwandu bikiri mu bihugu bya EU/EEA ndetse no mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe bikunze guha serivisi abaturage bakoresha akarere runaka, ni byiza ko amakuru ku barwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe aboneka mu buryo bwo gushyiraho amazina y'ibigo by'akarere ku rwego rwa 2 (NUTS-2).
Ubumenyi bw'u Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu biri mu bihe bya none bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi barwaye cyane bigomba rero kwitegura guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubwandu bukomeje mu baturage bwa SARS-CoV-2 no kwihanganira umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane cyane mu buvuzi, nk'uko byagenze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, bwihuse kandi bwuzuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, hamwe no guhindura uburyo bwo gukumira no kugabanya, kuko iyo bidashyizwe mu bikorwa hakiri kare, ukwiyongera kwihuse kw'umubare w'ibyabaye bishobora kutaha igihe gihagije abafata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugirango basobanukirwe, bemere kandi bahindure ibisubizo byabo.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rigaragaza ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Hari igihe gito cy'amahirwe ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu bikorwa byo kugenzura kugira ngo bigabanya umuvuduko wo gukwirakwira kwa SARS-CoV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo ku buvuzi.
Iyo ibyo bitabaye, birashoboka ko mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zishobora guhura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
