Nyuma, twagerageje kwerekana ko Remdesivir ishobora kurwanya izindi virusi z'umusemburo umwe wa RNA, harimo MERS na SARS.
Ishingiye kuri ibyo, Gilead yahaye uru ruganda Ubushinwa kugira ngo rukore igerageza ry'urubyiruko rwanduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Baricitinb, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin byasabwe nk'uburyo bushoboka bwo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye by'ubuhumekero.
Nyuma yo gufatanya imiti na Lopinavir/Ritonavir, indwara z'umwijima, iseseme, kugira iseseme, kwangirika kw'umwijima n'ibindi bishobora kubaho.
Iterambere ry'ubu buryo hamwe n'indi miti ikoreshwa mu barwayi, bigomba gukurikiranwa cyane.
Guteza imbere plasma n'imyanya ndangagitsina mu barwayi bakize
Hari amateka maremare yo gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara zandura kugira ngo bavurwe abandi barwayi bafite indwara imwe cyangwa barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwandura iyi ndwara.
Mu by'ukuri, abarwayi bakize akenshi bagira ibipimo byo mu maraso birenze urugero by'abanduye indwara.
Antibodies ni immunoglobulin (Ig) ikorwa na B lymphocyte mu kurwanya mikorobe n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga, kandi zimenya molekile z'indwara z'ubwoko bwose kandi zikayihosha mu buryo butaziguye.
Bishingiye kuri ibyo, plasma yakuwe mu maraso y'itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze bayinjiza mu barwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byagiye bihinduka mu masaha 24, kandi byaje kujyana no kugabanuka kw'ubuhumekero n'umutwaro wa virusi, ndetse no kongera umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko kandi, imiti yihariye ntiraboneka kandi hakenewe igenzura no gusobanura mbere yo gutanga uburyo bwo gukoresha ku bwinshi.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibibazo bimwe na bimwe bijyanye na plasma bigomba gusuzumwa neza bitewe n'ingaruka z'ubuvuzi.
Urugero, abanduye bashobora gutuma umubiri urushaho kugira ibyiyumvo byo kurwanya indwara, kandi bakagira indwara yo kugabanya imikorere y'utugingo tw'umubiri (cytocin release syndrome), uburozi bushobora kwica.
Umubare w'abanduye mu maraso ubusanzwe uba uri hasi, kandi hari ubushake bwinshi bwa plasma mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye cyane.
Guhanga no gukora vuba za 'antibodies' mu bihe bimwe na bimwe byo kurwanya icyorezo cy'isi biragoye.
Ku bw'ibyo, kwicamo ingirabuzimafatizo za B mu barwayi bakize no kugenzura ibimenyetso by'umubiri bigira ingaruka ku poroteyine z'ingenzi za virusi cyangwa kumenya kode za jenoside zisobanura ibimenyetso by'umubiri bifite ingaruka ku murwayi, ni ingenzi kandi ni ingirakamaro.
Muri ubwo buryo, dushobora kongera mu buryo bworoshye uburyo bwo gukora za rukingo.
Ubushinwa bwakoresheje TCM mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye mu gihe cy'imyaka ibihumbi.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka zabyo ahanini zishingira ku guhuza ibintu byinshi mu buryo bumwe, buhinduka bitewe n'uburwayi bushingiye ku nyigisho za TCM.
Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bikora ntabwo bizwi cyangwa ntibisobanutse, kubera ko ibyo bikoresho cyangwa imirwi yabyo ikora neza bigoye kuvumbura no kugenzura.
Muri iki gihe, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti y'ingenzi yo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje kugeza ku rugero, cyangwa abakize indwara zikomeye, kubera ko nta miti ihamye kandi ikora ya COVID-19.
Urugero, byavuzwe ko udufunguro twa Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen ari two twagize ingaruka nziza mu kuvura COVID-19.
Mu ntara nyinshi z'u Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19 ku kigero cya 87%, harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), naho mu ntara ya Hubei, TCM yakoreshejwe ku kigero cya 30% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19, ni ho hakoreshejwe TCM ku kigero cyo hasi cyane (13%).
Ariko, ni igereranya rikomeye cyane kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'uburemere, bigomba gushyirwa mu igenzura.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bugereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ibanze bwa WM na TCM n'ubuvuzi bw'iburengerazuba (WM).
Babonye ko igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, guhosha ibimenyetso no kujya mu bitaro cyari gito cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'iryo mu itsinda rya WM gusa.
Igishishikaje cyane, ni uko igipimo cy'ibimenyetso byo kugabanuka (byoroheje kugeza ku bikomeye) byari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%) kandi igipimo cy'urupfu cyari hasi cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Nyamara, ubudahangarwa n'ubushobozi bwa TCM biracyategereje kugeragezwa ku kigero kinini no mu bigo byinshi.
Bizashimisha kandi kumenya uburyo bukora, kandi niba bishoboka, gusobanura ibintu by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa guhuza.
Abenshi mu barwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 bagira ubwoba bw'indwara yandura cyane ndetse ishobora no guhitana ubuzima, kandi abantu bari mu kato na bo bakunze kugira ubwiherero, irungu n'umujinya.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'indwara nk'umuriro mwinshi, impiswi, inkorora n'ingaruka mbi z'imiti nk'ibitotsi biterwa na corticosteroids, bishobora gutuma umuntu agira imihangayiko n'ihungabana.
Mu byiciro bya mbere by'icyorezo cya SARS, hari ibimenyetso byinshi byo mu mutwe byavuzwe, birimo kwiheba igihe kirekire, guhangayika, guhungabana, kwishimisha kwa psychomotor, ibimenyetso bya psychotic, delirium ndetse no kwiyahura.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, gukurikirana no kugena abantu ku gahato bishobora gutuma abantu bahangayika cyane kandi bakumva bafite ikosa ry'ingaruka z'ubwandu, ku kutagwa mu kato no ku bantu bo mu miryango yabo n'inshuti zabo.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abakekwaho, n'abahuye na bo, ndetse n'abandi bantu muri rusange bakeneye ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe, bagomba guhabwa ubufasha.
Ubufasha bw'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe mu nzego zitandukanye z'ubuvuzi, itumanaho ryiza ririmo amakuru ya buri gihe kandi akwiriye ku ndwara ya SARS-CoV-2 n'imigambi y'ubuvuzi, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki by'umwuga no kwirinda guhura cyane.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ngombwa mu guhagarika ikurikiranya ry'ubwandu bw'amatungo n'abantu banduye, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa nk'inkunga mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa na virusi.
Hakozwe imbaraga mu gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S zo gukora za antibody ziramba kandi zikomeye zihagarika SARS-CoV no / cyangwa gukora ubudahangarwa bwo kurinda.
Urukingo rwa SARS rufite ubushobozi bwo guhosha indwara mu buryo bwa Live-Atenuated vaccine rwakozwe mu ngero z'inyamaswa.
Ariko mbere yo gutangira kwiga mu buvuzi, ubushobozi bw'abakandida b'urukingo mu bantu bakuze no mu ngero z'icyorezo, n'umutekano wabo ku banduye virusi z'inyamaswa ku bantu, ntibyigeze byemezwa.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS imaze imyaka 17 irangiye kandi nta bandi bantu bashya banditswe.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, hari ibindi bibazo n'indwara ya MERS bikomeje kugaragara mu Burasirazuba bwo hagati, kandi bikomeje gukwirakwira mu tundi turere bitewe n'ubwoko bw'ubwandu mu duce turimo indwara.
Uburyo bwo gukingira MERS bwakoreshejwe hakoreshejwe virusi zidakora, ADN plasmid, virusi, nanoparticules, udukoko tumeze nka virusi na poroteyine zisubiwemo, kandi zimwe muri zo zisuzumwa mu nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwiza kandi rukora neza rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu badafite ubwirinzi ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo gikomeje.
Icyakora, gutsinda iki kibazo biragoye kubera igihe kirekire (ku kigereranyo cy'amezi 18) gikenewe mu gukora urukingo no guhinduka kwa CoV.
Nk'indwara idasanzwe, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye kwiyongera ku barwayi ibihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi batagira uburwayi bw'ibanze barashobora gukira buhoro buhoro.
Ariko kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 ifitanye isano no kurwara cyane no gupfa mu barwayi barembye.
Niyo mpamvu, ni ngombwa ko ibigo by'ubuzima byubaka uburyo bwo guhanura iyi ndwara kugirango bashyire imbere serivisi zabo, cyane cyane mu turere dufite amikoro make.
