Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo yari ingenzi mu gutuma SARS igira ingaruka mbi, nk'uko byagenze kuri COVID-19.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866 bavuzwe haruguru, COVID-19 yibasiwe cyane n'abantu bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 30-65, aho 47.7% by'abarwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50.
Abarwayi bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kugira izindi ndwara ziterwa n'indwara kandi bafite ibibazo kandi bari bakuze cyane ugereranyije n'abandi (imyaka 66 ugereranyije n'imyaka 51), byerekana ko imyaka ari yo igaragaza uko indwara igenda igenda mu ndwara ya COVID-19.
Igitsina: Ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 mu bagabo bwari bwinshi cyane ugereranyije n'ubw'abagore (0.31/100,000 vs 0.27/100,000), nkuko byavuzwe haruguru.
Kuba hari indwara nyinshi n'ibibazo by'indwara: Abarwayi bafite COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane barushaho kurwara umutima cyane no kugira arrhythmias.
Byongeye kandi, indwara z'umutima ni zo z'ingenzi mu bituma abarwayi ba SARS bapfa.
Byongeye kandi, byatangajwe ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no guhuza na cholangite ifite ACE2-positive, bigatuma impyiko zidakora neza mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Tugomba kwibuka ko imyaka n'indwara ziterwa na yo bifitanye isano ikomeye kandi ko bishobora guhungabana.
Amakuru adasanzwe aboneka mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi: Ibipimo bya poroteyine igira ibyiyumvo bya C (CRP) mu maraso bigaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa imvune mu mitsi kandi byatanzwe nk'ikimenyetso cy'umuvuduko ushobora gutera indwara, ibisubizo by'ubuvuzi no gukira burundu.
Hatanzwe kandi inama ku bijyanye n'ihura ry'ibipimo bya CRP n'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Byongeye kandi, kongera lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) birashobora no gufasha mu kwemeza ingaruka.
Ibi binini by'indwara byigaragaza cyane mu ngingo nyinshi, cyane cyane mu mutima n'umwijima, kandi birasohoka mu gihe habayeho kwangirika kw'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Bityo rero, ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe by'umutima cyangwa impyiko zidakora neza.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubushakashatsi: Kugira ngo hamenyekane neza ibibazo bya COVID-19 n'ingaruka zabyo, hagomba gufatwa ingamba zo kureba uko ibipimo by'ubuvuzi n'imikorere y'ibipimo by'ubuvuzi bigenda bihuzwa n'ibindi bibazo.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byasobanuwe haruguru, kugirango bigabanuke ubukana bw'ibyangiritse by'ubuhumekero, Steroids ni imiti yo kurwanya indwara ikoreshwa cyane nk'ubuvuzi bwunganira indwara zandura.
Kubera ko ibipimo byinshi bya corticosteroids byakoreshejwe cyane mu barwayi ba SARS ikomeye, abenshi mu barokotse barwaye ubumuga bwa Avascular Osteonecrosis bufite ubumuga burambye n'ubuzima budafite ubuzima bwiza.
Ku bw'ibyo, niba ari ngombwa, abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakwiriye gukoresha steroid mu doze nto kandi mu gihe gito.
Imihangayiko: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, abarwayi benshi mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 bakunze guhangana n'igihe kirekire cyo gushyirwa mu kato no kudacika intege bikabije, kandi bakumva ko bagize agahinda gaterwa no kubona abo mu muryango wabo na bagenzi babo bapfa.
Inama z'imitekerereze n'ubufasha bw'igihe kirekire ni ngombwa mu gufasha abo barwayi guhangana n'imihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu bugaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 gitandukanye na SARS.
Uretse kwigana mu gice cyo hasi cy'ubuhumekero, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwigana mu buryo bugira ingaruka nziza mu gice cyo hejuru cy'ubuhumekero kandi mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'ibanze, ishobora kugaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso, nk'uko bimeze ku zindi CoV ziterwa n'ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu bihe bya mbere cyangwa mu gihe cy'ubwandu bw'indwara bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu kazi kabo ka buri munsi, bigatuma kurwanya icyorezo bigorana cyane.
Icyakora, abantu benshi bari basanzwe batekereza ko SARS-CoV yandura iyo barwaye cyane, mu gihe ubwandu bwinshi butari bwaba mu byiciro bya mbere.
Muri ubwo buryo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 ubu kirakomeye cyane kandi kiragoye kugenzura ugereranyije n'icyorezo cya SARS.
Muri iki gihe, mu Bushinwa hari ingamba zikomeye, zirimo gufunga Wuhan n'imijyi ihakikije no gushyira abaturage hafi ya bose mu kato, mu rwego rwo guhashya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo izo ngamba zagize ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu no ku bindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragabanuka, bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo kigabanutse.
