Iyi virusi kandi yagaragaye mu musarani, igaragaza ko hashobora kuba hari ubwandu bushya bw'imyanda binyuze mu kanwa.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138, bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abarwayi bashobora kuba baratewe n'indwara zo mu muhogo (zaturutse mu bitaro), muri bo harimo abarwayi 17 bafite izindi ndwara za mbere n'abakozi 40 b'ubuzima.
Abantu, cyane cyane abavura, abakozi b'imiryango, abagize umuryango, abakozi bakorana ndetse n'abari hafi y'abarwayi cyangwa abanduye, bagomba gufata ingamba zo kwirinda.
Kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora gukoreshwa nk'urwego rwa mbere rw'ubwirinzi mu kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura; gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi n'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuhumekero bwa N95 (ingingo za #1860) bifasha mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turinda udutonyanga duto tw'umwotsi tuva ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye gukwirakwira mu mwuka cyangwa kuguma ku kintu, aho dushobora gukwirakwira ku bandi.
Ariko, udupfukamunwa twa N95 gusa (ingingo za #1860) ni two dushobora kurinda virusi nto cyane nko kuri 10 kugeza kuri 80 nm, 5% gusa ni zo zishobora kwinjira burundu; SARS-CoV-2 ifite ingano imwe na SARS-CoV kandi zombi ziri kuri 85 nm.
Kubera ko udukoko dushobora kwinjira no mu masike eshanu zikurikirana, abavura abarwayi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa twa N95 (ingingo za 1860s) aho kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi.
Uretse kwambara udupfukamunwa, abafasha mu by'ubuzima bagomba kwambara imyenda ikwiriye yo kwicungira mu buryo bw'ubwirinzi kugira ngo bakomeze kugabanya guhura n'ubwandu.
Iyi virusi ishobora no kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu jisho.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 nubwo yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95; virusi ishobora kuba yarinjiye mu mubiri we binyuze mu jisho rye ryanduye.
