Ihinduka n'ihinduka ry'imiterere byateje koranavirusi (CoV) n'ibinyabuzima byayo, harimo n'abantu, guhinduka mu myaka ibihumbi.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bafite virusi z'ubwandu bw'agakoko bagaragaye ko batera indwara z'ubwoko bworoheje nk'ibicurane.
Icyorezo cya SARS n'icyorezo cya MERS byashyize hasi icya mbere mu kugaragaza ko kwandura HCoV bishobora kwangiza no kwica.
Icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu Bushinwa bwo hagati mu mpera za 2019 cyongeye gutuma CoVs zongera kuvugwa cyane, kandi byadutangaje kubera ko zigaragaza ubwandu bwinshi n'ubwandu buke ugereranyije na mushiki wayo SARS-CoV.
Kwandura HCoV ni indwara yandurira mu matungo kandi gusobanukirwa inkomoko ya zoonotic ya HCoV bishobora kudufasha.
HCoVs nyinshi zituruka mu birura aho zidakunze gutera indwara.
Hari kandi n'izindi ndwara z'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwa HCoVs.
Kumenya intungamubiri mu matungo bigira ingaruka ku burinzi bw'ubwirinzi bw'abantu.
Gusuzuma itandukaniro ry'abanduye na CoV mu nyamaswa na byo bishobora gutanga ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku ndwara ziterwa na CoV mu bantu.
Muri iyi raporo, turatanga isesengura ry'ubumenyi buriho kuri HCoVs ndwi, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwazo, hamwe n'inkomoko yazo mu nyamaswa n'ubwandu buhuriweho.
Icy'ingenzi, turagereranya kandi turagereranya HCoV zitandukanye duhereye ku miterere ya virusi no kongera guhuza genome.
Muri iyi nkuru, havugwamo icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu.
Byongeye kandi, hakomeje kugaragara ko hakenewe impinduka nziza mu bahanga mu by'imiti, ndetse n'ingaruka z'ihindagurika rya virusi ku burwayi.
Koronavirusi (CoV-Cluster) ni zo mu muryango wa Koronoviride, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara z'umwanda, z'ubwoko bumwe, z'ubwoko bumwe bwa RNA.
"Bifite genome nini cyane muri virusi za RNA iri hagati ya kilobasi 26 na 32, izo virusi ziswe ""CoV"" kubera imiterere y'umubiri umeze nk'ikamba iri munsi ya mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki".
Mu buryo bw'imiterere, CoVs zifite genomes z'ingenzi z'umuryango umwe.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome bigizwe n'ibice bibiri binini by'inyuguti z'igitabo (ORF1a na ORF1b) bivuguruzanya, bihindurwa (translation) muri pp1a na pp1ab replicase polyproteins.
Izi poroteyine z'amoko menshi zikorwa mu buryo bwo gukora izindi poroteyine 16 zitari iz'ubwubatsi, zitiriwe nsp1~16.
Mu gice gisigaye cya genome, ORF ifitemo poroteyine z'ibanze zirimo insinga (S), umwenda (E), uruhu (M) na nucleoproteins (N).
Poroteyine zimwe na zimwe z'inyongera zihariye ku murongo wa CoV na zo zanditseho imirongo itandukanye ya CoV.
Bitewe n'itandukaniro ry'imiterere ya poroteyine, CoVs zashyizwe mu matsinda ane (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV na delta-CoV), aho beta-CoVs ari zo HCoVs nyinshi mu matsinda kandi igabanyijemo imiryango ine (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya byerekana ko udukoko n'imbeba ari byo bitanga ibinyabuzima byinshi bya alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga ibinyabuzima byinshi bya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, CoVs zakomeje kunyura mu nzitizi z'amoko, zigerageza kuba zimwe mu ndwara z'ingenzi ku bantu.
