Mu Ukuboza 2019, icyorezo cya 2019 cya Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) cyatangiye, cyitiriwe byemewe n'amategeko Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) kandi virusi yitwa Severe Acute Respiratory Syndrome Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, OMS yashyize COVID-19 mu rwego rw'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye igitabo cy'inama yihuse cyasohotse kuri interineti ku itariki ya 06 Gashyantare 2020 mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare.
Kuva yasohoka, hari abantu benshi cyane bayitabiriye.
Twibuke ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubumenyi bushingiye ku byamenyekanye mu buvuzi n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi, bityo, uburyo bwo gusuzuma no kuvura bugenda buvugururwa.
Urugero, mu mabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), kuva ku ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, hasohotse amavugurura arindwi, buri rimwe rifite ibintu bimwe na bimwe rihindura.
Ubu Zhou na bagenzi be batanze igitekerezo ku mabwiriza yacu, batanga igitekerezo cyo gutanga amanota yoroshye ashingiye ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Ibikorwa byabo byongeyeho ibimenyetso bishya mu mabwiriza yacu kandi byerekana ibintu by'ingenzi byerekeranye n'iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Turabashimira kandi turabashimira ku bw'ibikorwa byabo by'ingenzi.
Ariko kandi, bagomba no kuvugurura ibyo bakora bagakurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi ya COVID-19 (igeragezwa rya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi bugezweho.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'ibwirizwa rya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo haboneke umuntu ukekwaho ubwandu, isesengura ryimbitse rigomba kuba rifite ibimenyetso bibiri by'ubwandu hamwe n'ibimenyetso by'amateka y'icyorezo, cyangwa se niba nta mateka y'icyorezo asobanutse, ibipimo bitatu by'ubwandu bigomba kuzuzwa.
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'abatuye cyangwa bagendera mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu bice biyikikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho COVID-19 imaze kumenyekana mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) amateka y'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 (bafite ikizamini cya nucleic acid cyemeza ko banduye); (3) amateka y'abanduye bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa mu bice biyikikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho COVID-19 imaze kumenyekana mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) amateka y'abanduye mu matsinda yemejwe (kugirango barwaye umuriro mu byumweru 2 cyangwa hejuru y'aho, mu bice bito nk'ingo, ibiro, ishuri, icyumba cy'ishuri, no mu byumba by'amashuri)
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso by'ubwonko biranga ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) Umubare w'amaraso yera yose mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bya mbere by'uburwayi ugaragaza umubare usanzwe, wagabanutse cyangwa wagabanutse w'indwara ya lymphocyte.
Kugira ngo haboneke umuntu wemejwe ku mpamvu z'uburwayi, hagomba kuba hari ibimenyetso by'ubwandu cyangwa ibimenyetso bya seriyoloji byerekana ko: (1) SARS-CoV-2 yemeza ko yanduye mu isuzuma rya PCR ry'igihe nyacyo; (2) kugira homogeneity cyangwa imiterere ihwanye n'iyo virusi ya coronavirus izwi mu buryo bwuzuye; (3) ibimenyetso bya IgM antibody na IgG antibody by'umwihariko bya SARS-CoV-2 mu isuzuma rya samoa; cyangwa IgG antibody ya SARS-CoV-2 y'umwihariko yanduye ikava ku itabona, kandi ikagira umuvuduko ≥4 mu gihe cy'uburwayi no mu gihe cy'uburwayi.
Twabonye ko mu cyiciro cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020) harimo ibipimo bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo byerekana nucleic acid mu myanya y'ubuhumekero n'ibipimo by'amaraso.
Kumenya indwara z'ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu cya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma igihamya cya seroloji cyongerewe mu cyiciro cya karindwi.
Ibi bihinduka bishingiye ku gikorwa gikomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi cyo gushaka ibipimo by'amaraso hamwe n'ibipimo by'imiyoboro y'ubuhumekero kugirango bagerageze vuba icyuma cyiza cyo gupima acide nucleic, cyongera ibisubizo by'ibipimo bitandukanye kandi kifasha gutanga ibipimo byemeza ko hari abanduye.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso birushaho kwiyongera, bitwibutsa ko tugomba kwitondera abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bidasanzwe n'abadafite ibimenyetso.
Ku bw'ibyo, Zhou na bagenzi be bagombye kuvugurura urutonde rw'ibimenyetso by'imiyoborere, kuko bashyize mu byiciro by'abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi ko bafite ibyago bike.
Iyi mibare ikeneye no kwemezwa mu bushakashatsi no mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi.
Mu gusoza, twizeye ko hazabaho ibindi bimenyetso by'imvaho kandi abasomyi bazatumire kugira icyo batangaza.
Mu gusuzuma abemejwe ko banduye n'abatekereza ko banduye, turasaba ko bakorwaho ubushakashatsi kandi bagakurikiza amabwiriza agezweho mu bihugu byabo.
Ikipe yacu izajya igeza ku bantu amabwiriza mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo ibafashe.
Bangladesh yatangaje ko imaze kugira umubare munini w'abantu bapfa ku munsi bishwe na COVID-19.
Ejo, Bangladesh yemeje ko hari abantu batanu bashya bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye ku munsi umwe bazize iyi virus.
Ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe indwara, kugenzura no gukora ubushakashatsi ku ndwara (IEDCR) cyatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye banditswe ukubiyemo 114 bari mu bikorwa n'abamaze gukira 33 bari mu ngo zabo.
Abantu 17 ni bo bamaze gupfa.
Mu kiganiro n'itangazamakuru, Dr Meerjady Sabrina Flora, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, yavuze ko mu bapfuye harimo abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dr Mirzadi yavuze ko babiri muri bo barengeje imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60 naho umwe ari hagati y'imyaka 41 na 50.
Yongeyeho ko babiri mu barwayi bari baturutse i Dhaka.
