Mu itangazo ryashyizwe kuri videwo kuri uyu wa Gatandatu, Minisitiri w'ubwikorezi bw'imihanda n'ibiraro wa Bangladesh, Obaidul Kader, yavuze ko imodoka z'abaturage zizamara igihe kirekire zifunze kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe mbere kugeza ku wa Gatandatu utaha.
Ihagarikwa ry'ibigo by'ubucuruzi ryatangiye ku wa 26 Werurwe, kandi ryari riteganyijwe kurangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
Ingendo z'ibintu by'ingenzi nk'imiti, lisansi n'ibiribwa byari byemewe.
Ku ya 8 Werurwe, abantu babiri bagarutse mu Butaliyani n'umugore wa umwe muri bo ni bo ba mbere mu gihugu cya Bangladesh banditsweho icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, kugeza ubu abo bantu uko ari batatu bamaze gukira.
Umubare w'abanduye SARS-CoV-2 ku isi urenga miliyoni
Amakuru ya Johns Hopkins University agaragaza ko imibare y'abanduye coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ku isi yose yarenze miliyoni ku wa Kane.
Nibura abantu 52,000 bapfuye bahitanwe n'indwara iterwa na coronavirus, COVID-19.
Iki gikorwa gikomeye cyabaye ku munsi umwe na Malawi yemeje ubwandu bwa mbere bwa coronavirus ndetse n'urupfu rwa mbere rwa coronavirus muri Zambia.
Kugeza ku wa Kane, Koreya ya Ruguru yari yatangaje ko ari kimwe mu bihugu bike byasigaye bitanduye coronavirus.
Kugeza ejo, OMS yanditse abantu 1,051,635 banduye mu masaha 24 ashize, barimo 79,332 ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi za mu gitondo ku isaha yo mu Burayi bwo hagati (0800 UTC).
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, hamaze kwandura coronavirus ibihumbi 244 byiyongera ku bantu nibura 5,900 bapfuye.
CBS News, ivuga ko abantu barenga 1000 bamaze gupfa muri Amerika ku wa Gatatu bishwe na coronavirus, ivuga ko ibivugwa n'ikigo cya Johns Hopkins University.
Hirya no hino ku isi, ibihugu byatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
Ku wa Kane, Meya wa Moscou Sergei Sobyanin yongeye igihe cyo gufunga umujyi kugeza ku ya 1 Gicurasi.
Ku rwego rw'igihugu, Perezida Vladimir Putin yatangaje ko amafaranga azakomeza kwishyurwa n'abanyarwanda batagiye ku kazi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
