Arabiya Sawudite yongereye amasaha yo gutaha mu mijyi yera ya Mecca na Medina, aho amasaha y'ikiruhuko yari asanzwe ari 3pm kugeza 6am gusa.
Thailand yari iteganyije gushyiraho amasaha yo gutaha kuva saa kumi z'ijoro kugeza saa yine za mu gitondo.
