Amaduka yo muri Australia yagabanyije umubare w'impapuro z'isuku ku bucuruzi
Ku Cyumweru no ku wa Gatandatu nimugoroba, amaduka yo muri Australia yitwa Woolworths na Coles yagabanyije imipaka yo kugura impapuro z'isuku ku bucuruzi ku maduka yose ku rwego rw'igihugu, ku buryo byibura abiri na paketi imwe.
Byongeye kandi, ALDI yatangije umurongo wa pakiti imwe muri Nzeri.
Ibi bihano byashyizwe nk'ubutumwa ku masoko no ku rupapuro rwa Facebook rw'uru ruganda.
Abaguzi bavuga ko bari mu bubiko bwo gutunga ibintu kubera gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe abantu bari mu kato.
Ku wa gatatu, Woolworths na yo yagabanyije igiciro cy'impapuro z'isuku zo kohereza mu ngo, igatanga isahani imwe ku icumbi.
Izi mpinduka zikurikira impinduka z'ibya mbere mu bicuruzwa by'ibikoresho bine byatangijwe na Woolworths na Coles ku ya 4 na 5 Werurwe.
Ku ya 8 Werurwe, Calls yatangaje ko ibihano byo gufunga amakarito ane byatangiye mu duce dutandukanye, ariko "mu maduka menshi, byose byatangiye kugurishwa mu gihe cy'isaha imwe nyuma yo gutangwa", avuga ko ibyo bisabwa ari "bitigeze bibaho", mu butumwa bwo kuri Facebook ku wa kabiri kuri ALDI, avuga ko ari "bitunguranye".
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Woolworths, mu cyumweru gishize, ibicuruzwa byariyongereye cyane.
Ibitaro bya Costco i Canberra byemerewe kwakira amasahani abiri mu cyumweru gishize.
Kugira ngo kongerera umubare w'ibura, Coles isaba ibicuruzwa byinshi cyane ku bakiriya bayo kandi ikongera umubare w'ibikoresho, Woolworths isaba ibicuruzwa byinshi, ALDI igatanga ibicuruzwa mbere y'uko ku wa Gatatu wihariye uteganijwe.
Umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi muri Australia, Russell Zimmerman, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko ya leta yo mu karere ko gutumiza ibicuruzwa mu modoka atuma ibyo bigoye.
Yiteze ko ibiciro by'umusaruro bizamuka uko abaguzi bazagerageza guhaza ibisabwa.
ALDI yatangaje ku wa kabiri ko nyuma yo kuva mu bubiko mbere, amaduka amwe n'amwe adashobora gukora ibicuruzwa byihariye ku wa gatatu.
Mu nkuru yatanzwe na News.com.au, Dr Gary Mortimer, impuguke mu bucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi muri kaminuza y'ikoranabuhanga ya Queensland, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuza ibicuruzwa byayo buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'isuku ari ibintu biremereye bituma ibikorerwa muri ibyo bigo biba bike cyane, kandi ko igihe byose biba byarangiye, intebe nini cyane zisigara zisigaye ari ubusa, bigatuma abantu barushaho kumva ko hari ibyo badafite.
Nkuko byatangajwe na ABC News, "Coles na Woolworths bavuga ko niba afite ibintu byinshi, ibintu nka 'toilet roll' na 'sanitizer' [bishobora kugurwa], kandi bifite byinshi, ubwo ubwoba bushobora kugabanuka", Russell Zimmerman.
Ku wa Gatatu, ikigo cy'ubucuruzi bw'impapuro z'isuku zisubiwemo cyavuze ko ibyangombwa byacyo bigiye kurangira.
Nkuko byatangajwe na News.com.au, Kimberly-Clark, ikora ibikoresho by'isuku bya Klinex na Solaris Paper, ikora ibinyobwa, yemeza ko ikora amasaha 24 ku munsi kugira ngo ibyibuze.
Urubuga rw'imicungire y'imitungo Domain.com rwatangaje ko hari abagurisha imitungo batanga impapuro z'isuku ku buntu ku wa mbere ugiye gucuruza muri cyamunara i Melbourne, zimwe muri zo zikaba zatanzwe kubera ko abaguzi bari mu biruhuko mu mpera z'icyumweru kirekire cy'umunsi w'akazi.
Kuri uyu wa kane, mu kinyamakuru cya NT News, cyandikwa buri munsi mu rurimi rw'Icyongereza, hari inyandiko y'amapaji umunani yo gutabara, igenewe gukata ibitabo by'imfashanyigisho, maze bikakoreshwa nk'impapuro z'isuku.
Ku ya 3 Werurwe, raporo ya ABC Australia yavuze ko amaduka yari yanze gushyiraho ibihano, aho yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyiraho ibihano ku bicuruzwa.
Russell Zimmerman yavuze ko hari ibindi bikoresho byifuzwa cyane, birimo udupfukamunwa, imiti yo guhanagura, ibicuruzwa byumye, imyenda yo gukaraba intoki n'ifu.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, hanze ya Ositaraliya, ku Cyumweru nimugoroba, ku isoko ryo mu Bwongereza ryitwa Okado, ku mbuga za interineti, kugurisha impapuro z'isuku z'ibikoresho by'isuku bya Andres bihabwa imipaka ibiri y'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'isuku.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 ari icyorezo.
"Nubwo ijambo ""icyorezo"" ridasobanura uko indwara runaka iteye ahubwo risobanura uko icyorezo icyo ari cyo cyose cyakwirakwiriye, OMS yavuze ko ari ngombwa ko ubutegetsi bufata ingamba:"
"Ibihugu byose biracyafite ubushobozi bwo guhindura icyorezo cyugarije isi".
"Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa OMS, Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko niba ibihugu bishobora kumenya, "" gupima, kuvura, gushyira mu kato, kumenya no guhuza".
"Turahangayikishijwe cyane n'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo ndetse n'imiterere y'ubucucike bwacyo".
"Dore uko Dr Tom Friedan, umuyobozi wa mbere w'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo cyugarije isi yose ari "icya mbere".
Mu magambo yatangarije CNN muri Gashyantare, yagize ati "Nta virusi y'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero, uretse ibicurane, yagiye ikwirakwira ku isi kuva itangirira".
Gabrèsas nawe yagize ati "Ntitwari twigeze tubona icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus mbere".
Yakomeje agira ati "kandi nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo cy'isi yose gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iki cyorezo gishya cyabaye icyorezo ku isi, gikurikiye icyemezo cyafashwe na OMS cyo gutangaza ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima bw'abaturage mu rwego rw'isi mu kwezi kwa mbere.
Dr. Anthony Fauci, umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cya Amerika Gishinzwe Indwara z'Ibitera Mbonera n'Ibindi Byakwirakwira, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kizaba kibi cyane".
Ikinyamakuru Associated Press cyatangaje kuwa kane ko umubare w'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ku isi uri ku kigero cya 126,000, bikaba byarateje impfu zisaga 4,600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), iterwa n'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2.
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyatangajwe ko ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu buzima ku rwego mpuzamahanga ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020 ndetse kizafatwa nk'icyorezo ku isi ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere tw'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, bihitana abantu bagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364,000 bamaze gukira.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'abapfa ku bwandu bwa coronavirus itegerejwe kuri 4%, mu gihe ku isi yose, imibare iri hagati ya 13.04% muri Algeria na .08% muri New Zealand.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo bishobora kuba bikubiyemo amapfupfa na syndrome y'ihungabana rikomeye mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Ubusanzwe kuva ku muntu wahuye n'iki cyorezo kugeza igihe ibimenyetso bitangiriye, bitwara iminsi itanu, ariko bishobora gutwara iminsi iri hagati y'ibiri n'icumi n'ine.
Nta rukingo cyangwa imiti yihariye ya virusi.
Ubuvuzi bw'ibanze ni ubuvuzi bw'ibimenyetso n'ubufasha. Ingamba zo kwirinda zisabwa zirimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka mu maso mu gihe ukorora, kugendera kure abandi bantu, no kwitegereza no kwicungira abantu bakekwaho kuba banduye.
Abategetsi ku isi yose bitabiriye ibihano byo kugenzura ingendo, kugenzura umutekano, kugenzura ibyago mu kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Icyorezo cyugarije isi cyateje ibibazo bikomeye by'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza ku isi, imyidagaduro, ibikorwa by'idini, politiki n'umuco birahagarikwa, kandi ibicuruzwa byuzuye ubwoba byongereye ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe haba ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu karere mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku bice 99.4% by'abanyeshuri bose ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi hari amacakubiri n'ivangura byibasira abandi bantu bo mu Bushinwa, mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo y'uburasirazuba bwa Aziya, bitewe n'ubwoko n'isura, ndetse n'abandi baturutse mu duce twiganjemo abantu banduye.
Kubera ko ingendo n'inganda zikomeye byahagaze, umwuka uhumanye n'imyuka ihumanya ikirere byagabanutse.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) mu Bushinwa, batangaje ko hari itsinda ry'abantu banduye indwara y'ibicurane bitamenyekanye ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, ndetse batangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abenshi mu banduye bafatiwe mu isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, bityo bikekwa ko iyi virusi yavuye mu matungo.
Virusi yateje iki cyorezo izwi nka SARS-CoV-2, ni virusi ivumburwa iherutse guhuzwa cyane na Coronavirus y'ikiboko, Coronavirus ya Bonroy na SARS-CoV. Umuntu wa mbere wagaragaweho ibimenyetso, nyuma yaje kumenyekana ko arwaye ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; kandi nyuma yaho nta sano riboneka uwo muntu yari afitanye na Wet Market Cluster.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, isoko ryagaragaye ko rifite aho rihuriye na bibiri bya gatatu by'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ibanze.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, raporo idasobanutse yo mu kinyamakuru cya South China Morning Post yagaragaje ko umuntu w'imyaka 55 wo mu ntara ya Hubei, ushobora kuba ari we wa mbere w'ubwandu bw'iyi ndwara, bwabonetse ku ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019. Ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko ubwandu bushya bwagabanutse mu Bushinwa, ariko bwiyongera mu buryo butunguranye mu Butaliyani, Irani na Koreya y'Epfo, kandi ko umubare w'abanduye bashya hanze y'Ubushinwa warenze umubare w'abanduye bashya mu Bushinwa ku nshuro ya mbere.
Umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba waragabanyijwe, cyane cyane ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Gashyantare, hari umubare muto w'abanduye bagaragaye mu rubyiruko, abenshi muri bo bari munsi y'imyaka 19 na 2.4% by'abanduye ku isi. Patrick Valence, umujyanama wa siyansi mukuru w'Ubwongereza, ateganya ko 60% by'abatuye Ubwongereza bagomba kwandura mbere yuko ubushobozi bwo kwirinda bukoreshwa.
Mu buryo buhuje n'amategeko yemewe, umubare w'abanduye ni umubare w'abantu bose bapimwe bagasanga baranduye COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3% kandi ibihugu byinshi nk'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye n'u Busuwisi byari bifite politiki zemewe yo kudakora ibizamini ku bantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku ya 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko kugeza ku ya 23 Mutarama, 86% by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu Bushinwa butari bwabonetse, kandi ko ubwo bwandu butari bwemejwe ari bwo bwatumye haboneka 79% by'ubwandu bwanditswe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani warenze cyane uwo abategetsi bavugaga.
Imibare y'ibanze y'ibanze y'ubwandu (R0) bwa COVID-19 yari 1.4 kugeza kuri 2.4 mu ntangiriro.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, bwavuze ko bishoboka ko ari 5.7.
Abenshi mu barwayi ba COVID-19 barakira.
Mu bantu batabyiboneye, igihe cyo kuva ku ndwara kugera ku rupfu kigera ku minsi 6 kugeza kuri 41, aho icyiciro cy'ibanze ari iminsi 14.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bapfuye bazira COVID-19.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, 80% by'abantu bapfuye mu Bushinwa bari bafite imyaka 60 kuzamura, 75% muri bo bakaba bari basanzwe bafite indwara z'umutima n'igisukari. Imibare ya leta y'abantu bapfuye kubera COVID-19 muri rusange yerekana abantu banduye COVID nk'uko amategeko asanzwe abivuga.
Umubare w'abapfa kubera COVID-19 ushobora kuba munini cyane, kuko ushobora kutagira abantu bapfuye batakoze ibizamini - nko mu ngo, mu bigo byita ku barwayi n'ibindi.
Hari amakuru amwe n'amwe avuye mu Butaliyani avuga ko umubare w'abantu bapfuye mu gihe cy'icyorezo wikubye inshuro 4-5 umubare w'abantu bapfuye bishwe na COVID.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeye ko "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] ari ikigereranyo gito ugereranyije n'umubare nyakuri", ibyo bikaba byaravuzwe n'ibinyamakuru bitagira amakuru ku mibare iri hasi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika. Bene ibyo bisobanuro bidafite ishingiro bikunze kugaragara mu byorezo by'isi, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya H1N1. Urupfu rwa mbere rwemejwe ni urw'i Wuhan ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020.
Impamvu ya mbere y'urupfu hanze y'u Bushinwa ni uko ku itariki ya 1 Gashyantare, Filipine ari yo yabonye umuntu wa mbere wapfuye, naho ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, u Bufaransa ni bwo bwabonye umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Aziya.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga icumi na babiri bapfuye hanze y'u Bushinwa, ni bo bamaze kumenyekana muri Iran, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, abantu barenga mirongo ine mu bihugu n'uturere twose tw'isi, uretse Antarctica, bamaze gupfa.
Iyi mibare itandukana bitewe n'akarere, kandi biganisha ku gipimo cy'ibipimo, ubuziranenge bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza, igihe cyashize kuva icyorezo cyatangira, n'ibintu biranga abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima muri rusange. Imibare y'urupfu n'ubwandu igaragaza umubare w'abapfa ku gihe runaka ugabanyijwe n'umubare w'abanduye.
Dukurikije imibare ya Johns Hopkins University, imibare y'abamaze gupfa n'abanduye ku isi yose ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare w'abapfuye utandukanye bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'abamaze gupfa n'abamaze kwandura yavuye kuri 17.3% (bafite ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) igera kuri 0.7% (bafite ibimenyetso bya mbere kuva ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bipimo by'ubudahangarwa ni: imibare y'abamaze gupfa (CFR), igaragaza umubare w'abamaze kwandura bapfuye, n'umubare w'abapfuye kubera ubwandu (IFR) igaragaza umubare w'abanduye (bamaze kwandura cyangwa bataraboneka) bapfuye kubera ubwandu.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ihagarariye igihe icyo ari cyo cyose kandi ikurikirana abaturage runaka kuva ku banduye kugeza ku banduye binyuze mu gusesengura.
Intiti nyinshi zagerageje kubara imibare y'abantu runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso, gitekereza ko umubare w'abantu bapfa muri iki cyorezo uhera kuri 0.1% ukagera kuri 0.39%.
Imibare yo hejuru y'uru rwego ihuza n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Budage ku bipimo bya mbere bya COVID-19 byakozwe mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga no gusesengura ingaruka z'ibizamini ku miterere ya CFR.
OMS ivuga ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Ibihe ntarengwa n'igihe ntarengwa cyo gusohoka ntibyemezwa kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho umuntu ari.
