Ariko ubu, biragoye cyane kuvuga igihe ibyo bizabera.
"Zhong Nansan, umujyanama wa leta y'Ubushinwa mu by'ubuvuzi, yavuze ko bishobora kuba "birangiye muri Kamena" niba ibihugu byose byishyize hamwe bikurikiza inama z'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima mu gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi".
"Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu ishuri ry'isuku n'ubuvuzi bw'ikirere i Londres yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 ""ishobora gukomeza gukwirakwira mu gihe cy'umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri""".
