"William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati ""Ntekereza ko bidashoboka ko iyi koronavirusi, kubera ko ikwirakwira vuba cyane, ishobora kuzimira burundu"" kandi ko ishobora "guhinduka indwara y'igihe, igaruka buri mwaka".
