Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri by'ibanze ni umuriro (88%) n'ikinya (68%).
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara cyane ni: guhinda umushyitsi, guhumeka cyane (couf), kubura ubushobozi bwo guhumeka, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo no mu ngingo, kuribwa mu muhogo, umutwe, kugira imbeho, kugira iseseme, gusonza, guswera cyane, kuribwa cyane cyangwa cyanozis. WHO ivuga ko umuntu umwe muri batandatu arwara cyane kandi afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga urutonde rw'ibimenyetso byihutirwa by'ihumeka, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa guhindagurika, guhindagurika mu buryo butunguranye, kubyuka no kugira isura y'ubururu cyangwa iminwa; iyo ibimenyetso bihari, inama ni ugushaka ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi bwihuse.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kuba nta bimenyetso bafite, ariko ibipimo bigaragaza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagasaba ko abantu bahuye n'abantu banduye bakagenzurwa kandi bagakora ibizamini kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Ibipimo by'abashinwa ku kigero cy'abadafite ibimenyetso biri hagati ya bake na 44%.
Igihe cy'ikiringo gisanzwe cyo kuboneza urubyaro (igihe cy'ubwandu n'igiterwa n'indwara) ni iminsi iri hagati y'umunsi umwe n'iminsi 14; ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu. Mu rugero rw'ibihe bidashidikanywaho, igice cy'abantu bafite COVID-19 bagaragaje ko batakaje impumuro bwa mbere ni 30% na 15% mu bantu bagaragaje ko batakaje impumuro nyuma.
