Imyugariro irashobora guhanagurwa hamwe nibisubizo byinshi (muri minota imwe yo guhura n'imyanda ku gice cy'ibyuma bitagira ingeso), birimo 6271% ya ethanol, 50100% ya isopropanol, 0.1% ya sodium hypochlorite, 0.5% ya hydrogen peroxide, na 0.27.5% ya povidone-iodine.
Ibindi bikoresho nk'ibya benzalkonium chloride na chlorohexidine gluconate, ntabwo bikora neza cyane.
CDC irasaba ko mu gihe umuntu akekwaho cyangwa yemejwe ko yanduye COVID mu biro cyangwa mu bigo byita ku bana, ibiro, ubwiherero, ahantu rusange, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bikoreshwa hamwe, nk'amatabuleti, ecran z'umukono, konti, udukoresho two ku buryo bwa kure n'imashini za ATM zikoreshwa n'abantu barwaye, bikurwamo udukoko.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuzima avuga ko abantu bagomba gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru yabo cyangwa bakambara udupapuro tw'uruhu igihe bakoroye cyangwa batutse, kandi bakirinda gutakaza ako dupapuro.
Abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura bagirwa inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi. Kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ingano y'uduce tw'amazi dutangwa mu gihe tuvuga, twitsamura cyangwa dukorora.
OMS yatanze amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, impuguke mu by'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yavuze ko "gutera abantu udupfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ubushobozi bwo gukora ku maso, ari isoko ikomeye y'indwara iyo badafite isuku y'intoki".
OMS itera abantu basanzwe inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe gusa bafite ibyago byinshi, nk'abita ku muntu urwaye COVID-19, nubwo yemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukora ku maso.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, CDC itera inkunga y'imyambaro y'amasike y'amaso atari ay'ubuvuzi ikozwe mu myenda. Ubushinwa bwibanda cyane ku gukoresha amasike y'ubuvuzi ashobora gukoreshwa n'abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza, cyane cyane iyo begereye abandi bantu (metero 1 (ibirenge 3) cyangwa munsi yayo).
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe cy'ingendo mu modoka zitwara abantu benshi cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand barimo gukangurira abantu gukora udupfukamunwa mu ngo zabo no gukaraba buri munsi.
Mu gihugu cya Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakiya, abantu batambaye udupfukamunwa cyangwa udupfukamunwa, ntibakwiriye kujya hanze.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu duce dutuwe n'abantu benshi kugira ngo birinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yategetse ko abantu bose binjira mu maduka y'ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi bagomba kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bayo kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe cyose bagiye hanze.
Taiwan, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa tugera kuri miliyoni icumi buri munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, isaba abagenzi kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ngendo zo mu mihanda ya gari ya moshi na bisi z'amagana n'amajyaruguru guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe cyose bagiye hanze, kandi abadashobora kugura udupfukamunwa basabwe kwambara udupfukamunwa twakozwe mu ngo zabo.
Mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore, imyenda yo kwisiga mu maso ikoreshwa cyane.
Kwirinda kwitarura abandi (nanone bita kwitarura abantu ku mubiri) bikubiyemo kugabanya guhura cyane n'abantu no kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Muri izo ngamba harimo: kwishyirira mu kato; gukumira ingendo; gufunga amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade cyangwa amaduka.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda abantu mu gihe bari mu ngo zabo, bagabanya ingendo, bakirinda ahantu hari abaturage benshi, bakagira imishyikirano idahoraho, kandi bagakomeza gutandukanya abantu.
Ubu leta nyinshi zirasaba cyangwa zigatanga inama zo kwirinda abantu mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare w'abantu benshi bashobora guhurira hamwe ku biro bya leta ya Amerika n'ibigo nderabuzima, wagabanutse cyane uva ku bantu 250 (niba nta COVID-19 izwi muri ako karere) ugera kuri 50 hanyuma ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza abantu babiri cyangwa barenga guteranira hamwe. Abakuze n'abantu bafite indwara z'ibanze nk'indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso, no kubura ubudahangarwa bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara bikomeye no kurwara indwara ziterwa n'indwara, kandi CDC mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo mu baturage yabasabye kuguma mu rugo uko bishoboka kose. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'andi mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima batangiye gusimbuza imvugo "gutandukanya abantu" "gutandukanya abantu ku mubiri", bisobanurwa ko ari ugukomeza kugirana imishyikirano mu buryo busanzwe cyangwa mu buryo bw'imibanire".
"Icyatumye ikoreshwa ry'ijambo"kwirinda" (social distancing) ryiyongera cyane, aho gutera abantu inkunga yo gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo, byatumye abantu bareka kwifatanya n'abandi. Hari inzego zimwe na zimwe zatanze amabwiriza ajyanye n'ubuzima bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina ku bakoresha iki cyorezo".
Muri ibyo harimo no kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu ubana nawe gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Abantu bafite COVID-19 n'abatekereza ko bafite COVID-19 basabwe kwicumbikira mu rugo.
Ibigo by'ubuzima bitanga amabwiriza arambuye ku bijyanye no kwitarura abantu. Guverinoma nyinshi zitegeka cyangwa zigatanga inama yo kwitarura abantu bose batuye mu duce twibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura yashyizweho ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu baherutse guhura n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19 ndetse n'abaherutse gukora ingendo mu bihugu cyangwa uturere dufite ubwandu bwinshi, basabwe kwiherera mu kato k'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe baherukaga guhura.
Uburyo bwo guhashya icyorezo ni uguhagarika no kucyirukana.
Ingamba zo guhashya mu byiciro bya mbere by'icyorezo zirafatwa, kandi hagamijwe gutangiza no gukingira abantu banduye, uretse gushaka no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye, kugira ngo bahagarike ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu baturage basigaye.
Iyo nta bundi buryo bwo guhashya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo bushoboka, imbaraga zigenda zifata ku rwego rwo kugabanya: hari ingamba zifatwa mu kugabanya umuvuduko w'iki cyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka kigira ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi n'abaturage.
Ibi bishobora gutuma haba ingano y'ibipimo by'ubudahangarwa n'ibipimo by'ubudahangarwa.
Gucika kw'icyorezo ku rugero rwo hasi cyane ku buryo umubare w'ibinyabuzima byatangiriye ku mubare wa mbere uri munsi ya 1 ni kimwe mu bintu bikenewe mu guhangana n'icyorezo, bizwi nka "leveling the epidemic curve".
Iyo ibonetse, bigabanya ibyago byo kuvurwa, kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukingira no kuvura.
Bimwe mu bintu bishobora gutuma iki cyorezo kivaho mu buryo bunyuranye n'imiti, harimo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko kugira isuku y'amaboko, kwambara udupfukamunwa, no kwitarura abandi; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro; kwemera no gufatanya n'abaturage mu bindi bikorwa nk'ibyo; ndetse n'ingamba z'ibidukikije, nko gusukura. Nyuma y'uko icyorezo kigaragaye ko gikomeye, mu Bushinwa hatangijwe ingamba zikomeye zo guhashya iki cyorezo, nko gushyiraho icyorezo mu mujyi wose no guhagarika ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho ibizamini rusange n'igenzurwa ry'abantu mu gihugu, ndetse itanga n'amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu banduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye biyemeje kwihererana kandi igafatira ibihano bikomeye abananirwa kubikora.
Taiwan yongereye ibiciro byo kwambara udupfukamunwa no guhana ibihano ku bicuruzwa by'ubucuruzi by'ibihimbano.Ibikorwa by'Ubwongereza na Amerika bigaragaza ko guhosha (kugabanya ariko kudasenya icyorezo) no kugihagarika (kugabanya icyorezo) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Nubwo politiki yo kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo bya mbere ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu bakeneye serivisi z'ubuzima mu bice bibiri bya gatatu, n'urupfu mu gice cya kabiri, hari imibereho mibi mu nzego z'ubuzima, ihitana abantu babarirwa muri za miriyoni.
Gutegeka bishobora kuba inzira y'ibanze ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwabanje kubaho), kuko iyo ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu zidakoreshejwe, virusi ishobora kongera kwandura vuba.
Guteza ibibazo by'igihe kirekire mu guhashya icyorezo bitera ingaruka mbi mu rwego rw'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wemewe kuri COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuwukora harimo no kugerageza imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti igabanya uburibwe, kunywa amazi n'ikiruhuko bishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bw'uburwayi, umuganga w'umwuka wa ogisijeni, uruvange rw'amaraso (mu muhogo) n'ubufasha mu guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Iyo umuntu afashe siteroyi, bishobora kumugiraho ingaruka mbi kurushaho.
Hari imiti myinshi yemewe mu gihe cyashize mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwa virusi, ikomeje gushakishwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yatangaje ko hari imiti imwe n'imwe gakondo n'imiti yo mu rugo ifasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-19.
Kwiyongera kw'ubushobozi no kugura ibigo by'ubuzima ku barwayi ba COVID-19 byasobanuwe na WHO nk'ingamba zo kwirinda mbere na mbere icyorezo.
ECDC na WHO, Urwego rw'Akarere k'u Burayi, byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze, byerekana ko hakenewe gukuraho amasoko ku rwego rw'ibyiciro byinshi, harimo kongera igenzura rya laboratwari ku gupima COVID-19, gushyira mu kato no gutandukanya abarwayi bafite COVID-19 no kongera umubare w'abakurikiranwa cyane binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'imyuka n'ibitanda biboneka.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku cyateye iyi ndwara (ikitwa Patient Zero) gutangira.
Umuntu wa mbere wanduye coronavirus yavumbuwe ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu kwezi kumwe gusa, umubare w'abandura coronavirus muri Hubei wagendaga wiyongera.
Byinshi muri byo byari bifitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, aho inyamaswa nzima zagurishwaga, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi yavuye muri kimwe muri ibyo nyamaswa; cyangwa mu yandi magambo, ko ifite inkomoko y'inyamaswa. Ku ya 26 Ukuboza, umugera wa Pneumonia w'impamvu zitazwi wagaragaye, uvurwa n'umuganga Zhang Jixian mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, wabwiye CDC ya Wuhan Jianghan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
"Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan, baburiye bagenzi babo ku birebana n'"indwara ya koronavirusi isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, barashyizweho n'igipolisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, undi muganga Yi Feng na we ashinjwa n'abakozi be bakuru kubera ko yatanze imiburo.
Nyuma, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yatangaje itangazo ku mugaragaro ku ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha OMS.
Mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, i Wuhan hatangajwe umubare munini w'abanduye indwara y'ibicurane itaramenyekana, ikiri mu iperereza. Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya 2020, virusi yageze mu tundi duce tw'Ubushinwa, ifashijwe n'impunzi zo mu gihe cy'Ubunani, kandi kubera ko Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'umuhanda w'indarayi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje ko bwabonye abantu bashya 140 mu munsi umwe, barimo abantu babiri bo mu mujyi wa Beijing n'undi umwe wo mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Amakuru ya nyuma ya leta yerekanye ko kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu 6174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso. Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yari imaze kubona umubare munini w'abemejwe ku isi, irenga Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 9 Mata 2020, hari hamaze kuvugwa abarwayi barenga miliyoni 1.61 ku isi; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abantu barenga 364,000 barakize.
Hari nibura ubwandu bumwe mu bihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza kandi bishyiraho imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu kirimo ingamba z'igenzura nk'igenzura ry'abantu bose (zwi ku izina rya Guma mu rugo cyangwa Guma mu rugo cyangwa Guma mu rugo) na Guma mu rugo. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 cyangwa 90% by'abatuye isi, bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo na miliyari 1.3 bo mu Buhinde bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu bihe bimwe na bimwe byo gufunga, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri biyongera bagera kuri miliyari 2.6 - hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; ariko amakuru adafite gihamya aravuga ko umuntu wa mbere wemejwe yanduye COVID-19 ku ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jijian yabonye icyorezo cya Pneumonia ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, nyuma yo kubimenyeshwa n'ibitaro bye kuri Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwakozwe ku bipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko coronavirus imeze nka SARS.
Ku wa 31 Ukuboza, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yatangaje itangazo ku mugaragaro.
WHO yabimenyeshejwe uwo munsi.
"Nyuma y'uko ibyo bitangazamakuru bitangazwa, abapolisi bari baragabishije abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ko bashobora "gukwirakwiza ibihuha" ku cyorezo".
"Mu ntangiriro Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa yavuze ko nta "gihamya isobanutse" y'ubwandu bw'abantu".
"Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bw'impinduramatwara, nyuma yaho buvugwa ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yashyizweho na Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa, mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi".
"Kugenzura ingendo n'ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan byarahagaritswe maze ku ya 23 Mutarama hatangazwa gahunda yo kwirinda indwara, bivugwa ko ari "igikorwa cy'igenzura mu mateka y'abantu", cyagutse mu mijyi 15 muri Hubei, kigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zari zibujijwe muri uwo mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (ku ya 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce dutandukanye.
Abategetsi batangaje kandi ko imirimo yo kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Huyoshensan, yarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma y'ibitaro bya Leishenshan, hari ikindi cyubatswe kugira ngo kijye kwita ku barwayi benshi.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 byo muri Wuhan nk'ikigo cy'amakoraniro na sitade ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yafashe ingamba zo kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bakerarugendo no kwagura ikiruhuko cya Spring Festival.
Amashuri n'amashuri yisumbuye na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macao zagiye zifata ingamba, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu bice byinshi by'u Bushinwa, abantu bakoreraga kure.
Ingendo mu gihugu no hanze yacyo zari zihagaritswe.
Imodoka zitwara abagenzi mu gihugu hose zarahindutse, inzu ndangamurage zirafungwa by'agateganyo.
"Abagarijwe n'ibiza mu mijyi myinshi bari mu ngendo rusange, kandi abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bakekwaho kuba baragize ingendo z'inyuma zigenzurwa. Nyuma y'aho iki cyorezo cyerekeje ku isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira virusi "kuva mu bindi bihugu".
Urugero, Beijing yatangaje ko ingendo zose mpuzamahanga zinjira mu mujyi zigomba kumara iminsi 14 mu kato. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, hashize iminsi itanu gusa, hari umuntu umwe gusa wanduye mu Bushinwa bw'ibanze.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang, yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'ubwandu bwanduye mu gihugu mu by'ukuri ryahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo mu Bushinwa cyagenzurwa.
Nyuma y'amezi abiri y'ikomanze, ingendo mu gihugu cya Hubei zagiye zigabanuka ku munsi umwe, uretse i Wuhan. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko uburenganzira bwo kwinjira ku bantu bafite visa cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura buzahagarikwa guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, kandi nta bisobanuro by'igihe politiki izarangirira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Ubuyobozi bw'Ubushinwa bwashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda gufungura ku ya 30 Werurwe, ndetse butanga n'ingamba zo gufasha ibigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo watangiye saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo ku ya 4 Mata, hatangizwa iminota itatu y'agahenge mu gihugu hose, umunsi wa Qingming Festival, nubwo leta y'ibanze yasabye imiryango kwibuka ku rubuga rwa interineti, ikomeza kugendera kure kugira ngo irinde icyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habaye ukwiyongera gukomeye kw'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, ahanini biterwa n'idini rishya rya Daegu, ryitwa Shincheonji Church.
Abashyitsi ba Shinchangji Church bari baje mu rugendo rwo gusengera i Daegu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, 1,261 mu bayoboke 9,336 b'idini, cyangwa hafi 13%, batangaje ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje umuburo w'urwego rwo hejuru ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Korea yari imaze kugaragaza ubwandu bwemejwe burenga 2,000, buzamuka bujya ku ya 29 Gashyantare buza kugera ku 3,150.
Inzego zose z'igisirikare muri Koreya y'Epfo zatangiye kwihererana nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bagaragaweho ubwandu bwa virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangije gahunda yo gupima abaturage virusi no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye no gushakisha no gushyira mu kato abo bahuye nabo, gahunda ifatwa nk'iyari nini kandi iteguwe neza ku isi.
Uburyo bwo gupima burimo gutanga raporo y'ibimenyetso byawe bwite ku bantu bashya bavuye mu mahanga ukoresheje porogaramu igendanwa, gupima virusi ukoresheje test (drive through test) ku munsi ukurikiyeho no gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Nubwo imijyi itarashyizwe mu kato, gahunda muri Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'intambwe nziza mu kurwanya iki cyorezo. Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo wabanje kwihagararaho nyuma y'igisubizo cya Perezida Moon Jae-in kuri iki kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bemeje ko iki cyorezo cyakoreshejwe nabi mu buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, maze bashyira umukono ku nyandiko isaba ko Moon akurwaho cyangwa se bashimira uburyo yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi mu byumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko abantu bose bashya bavuye hanze bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri guhera ku ya 1 Mata.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yemeye ibyifuzo byo gupima virusi by'ibihugu 121.
Irani yatangaje ko yabonye abanduye SARS-CoV-2 bwa mbere ku ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho abantu babiri bapfuye bukeye bwaho, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi mu by'Ubuvuzi yabitangaje.
Mu ngamba z'ibanze zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco n'imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu no gufunga amashuri, ibigo by'amashuri makuru na za kaminuza.
Iran yatanze miliyari 5 z'amanyarwanda mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twatewe n'icyorezo, kandi ko abantu ku giti cyabo ari bo bonyine bazajya mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi yatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo ingendo nyinshi hagati y'imijyi zakomeje kubera ko Umwaka Mushya wa Persian wari ugiye gutangira.
Insengero z'aba Shiite muri Qom zari zifunguye kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibirego byo kugabanya ubwandu muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byemeje ko Iran ari yo soko y'ubwandu bwabo kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko ubwandu bwari hejuru cyane y'ubwandu 388 bwari bwaravuzwe na leta ya Irani kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
Ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yahagaritswe kubera ko 23 mu badepite 290 basanze basanzwemo virusi.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Umushakashatsi ku Burenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye abayobozi ba gereza muri Irani kurekura ku mugaragaro abarenga ku burenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu bafunzwe bazira kwitandukanya n'abandi mu mahoro, no gufungura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zibikwiriye.
Bivugwa ko ibigo byigaruriwe, nk'amabohero, aho ubuvuzi bukwiriye budahari, ari byo bishobora kugira ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virus.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, bakaba ari bo bantu benshi bapfuye muri icyo gihugu kuva iki cyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize icyo cyorezo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, coronavirus yatumye muri Iran haboneka abantu bashya 50 buri saha, n'undi umwe wapfa buri minota 10.
Umukozi wa OMS yavuze ko umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba ukubye incuro eshanu umubare w'abamaze kwandura muri Irani.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran bishobora kuba byangiza ubushobozi bw'icyo gihugu bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ushinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano bihanwa ibihugu byibasiwe cyane n'icyorezo byavanwaho, harimo na Iran.
Icyorezo cyamenyekanye ko cyatangiye mu Butaliyani ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga SARS-CoV-2 i Roma bagasanga baranduye.
Ibibazo byatangiye kwiyongera cyane, bigatuma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose ziturutse mu Bushinwa kandi igashyiraho ibihe bidasanzwe mu gihugu.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, mu ntara ya Lombardy, havumbuwe umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 nyuma y'abamaze kwemezwa ko ari 16 gusa. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yashyizeho itegeko rishya rigenga icyorezo, aho abantu barenga 50,000 baturutse mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani bashyizwe mu kato.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yavuze ko "kubera ko iki cyorezo cyateye, kwinjira no gusohoka mu duce twose bigiye guhagarikwa".
"Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifunga burundu ku rwego rw'igihugu kubera ko umubare w'abamaze gupfa mu Butaliyani ugeze ku 100".
Nubwo imikino ikomeye ya siporo, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yagombaga kuba mu buryo buciriritse kugeza muri Mata, ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bifungwa uretse supermarket na farumasi. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abaganga b'Abaganga b'Abaganga, Abashakashatsi, Abazamu n'Abavuzi b'Abaganga (SIAARTI) cyatanze inama ku mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi ku buryo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwa Trias Protocol.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwambutse Ubushinwa buza ku mwanya wa mbere ku isi mu bihugu byazahajwe na coronavirus, aho byahitanye abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, u Burusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'intambara mu Butaliyani zirimo ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 128,948, hapfuye 15,887 kandi habonetse abarwayi 21,815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN igaragaza ko kuba mu Butaliyani hari abantu benshi bageze mu za bukuru kandi bakaba batarabasha gupimwa, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye hapfa abantu benshi.
Ubwongereza bwabanje kugira igisubizo cyoroshye mu bihugu byahuye n'icyorezo, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, ubuyobozi bw'Ubwongereza ntibwari bwashyiriyeho abaturage babwo uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda cyangwa gushyira mu kato abantu benshi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yananiwe kumenya ingaruka z'iki cyorezo ku bantu. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko ingendo zose zidakenewe, imibonano mpuzabitsina n'ibindi bibujijwe, kandi ko yasabye abantu bose kwicara mu rugo aho bishoboka, no kwirinda utubari, resitora na za sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'ibiruhuko, nk'aho ari utubari na za siporo, bigomba gufungwa vuba bishoboka, kandi ko byasezeranyijwe ko 80% by'abakozi bazajya bahembwa amafaranga agera ku £2,500 buri kwezi mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ko hakwiye kubaho amabwiriza akomeye yo kwirinda abantu, kubuza abantu babiri cyangwa barenga guteranira hamwe no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze gusa ku bintu by'ingenzi.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwari busanzwe, izo ngamba zari zishobora kubahirizwa na polisi, binyuze mu gutanga amande no gukuraho abantu.
"Ubucuruzi bwinshi, harimo amaduka manini, amaduka y'imiti, amabanki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga, za lisansi n'amategura, byategetswe gufunga, uretse gusa ubucuruzi bwagaragaye ko ari 'bukenewe cyane.'"
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wari umaze kumenyekana ko yanduye COVID-19 muri leta ya Washington yo mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, yasubiye iwabo avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Inteko Rusange y'Umuryango wa Amerika ishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus yashyizweho ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ingutu mu buzima bw'abaturage, kandi bwubahiriza amategeko agenga abajya mu mahanga bavuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ikigo cy'ubuzima rusange cya leta ya US, cyatangaje ko cyateguye ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Nyamara, Amerika yakoze ibizamini buhoro cyane bituma umubare w'ubwandu nyabwo utamenyekana mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Ibizamini byasubitswe n'ibikoresho by'ibizamini byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, n'ibikoresho by'ibanze byakozwe na leta (amashuri, ibigo n'ibitaro) bitaremezwa na leta kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, kandi abantu bari bafite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura (kuva icyo gihe hakenewe icyemezo cya muganga) kugira ngo bagere ku rwego rwo kwemeza ikizamini kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko muri Amerika hari hasigaye ibizamini 4,000.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari hasigaye ibipimo 14,000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite amabwiriza ya muganga kandi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara bategereje amasaha menshi cyangwa iminsi myinshi kugira ngo bakore ibizamini". Ku ya 29 Gashyantare, nyuma yo kubona umuntu wa mbere wapfuye muri leta ya Washington muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko muri leta hashyizweho ibihe bidasanzwe, igikorwa cyahise gikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yafunze ibyiciro byayo muri Werurwe 3, kandi amashuri yose yo mu gihugu yose yatangiye gufunga mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'ibyorezo zo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College i Londres, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, zatanze inama ku ngaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus gishya mu gihugu no ku mitekerereze.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo kwishyura imishinga yo kwitegura no guhangana na coronavirus, ritanga miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari y'ingoboka ku bigo bya leta kugira ngo bihangane n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe ashyiraho imipaka ku ngendo z'abakozi, akahagarika inama no gushishikariza abakozi gukora bava mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'umwaka byahagaritswe.Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yashyizeho amategeko abuza ingendo mu Burayi hafi ya bwose, uretse mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 13 Werurwe mu gihe cy'iminsi 30.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye ibindi bihano ku Bwongereza na Ireland.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe by'ibiza mu gihugu hose, bituma hashyirwaho uburyo bwo gukoresha amafaranga ya federasiyo mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi mu rwego rwo guhashya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, umujyi wa New York wari ufite abarwayi 10,700 ba coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abarwayi bose bo muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko politiki yo kwirinda abantu ku buryo bwa bugufi igaragara ko ikora kuko imibare y'abanduye yagabanutse iva ku 2.0 ikagera ku 4.7 mu minsi mike.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe, umubare w'ubwandu muri New York City wari 32,308 hamwe n'abantu 672 bishwe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yari ifite umubare munini w'ubwandu bwa coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ku ya 8 Mata, umubare w'ubwandu muri Amerika wari 400,335 hamwe n'abantu 12,841 bapfuye.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru byo ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Donald Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera igihe cyo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort, bufite ibitanda 1000, bwashyize ingohe muri New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, muri Amerika hamaze kumenyekana abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24 ashize.
Kugeza ku ya 3 Mata, abantu barenga 100.000 baranduye muri leta ya New York. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kutagira icyo byitaho kuri icyo kimenyetso cy'akaga no kugenzura ubutumwa butangazwa n'abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu by'ubumenyi mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence, basaba guhuza imvugo n'ibitabo by'abantu ku giti cyabo bijyanye na virusi.
Impamvu y'ibanze y'uko Trump ashyigikiye imikorere y'ikibazo, yashyizwe ku ruhande n'amagambo y'ishyaka.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abatanga ibitekerezo banenze Amerika kubera ko ikoresha ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi cyane, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'ingenzi, biva mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'imikorere y'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu gukora no guhanura uburyo bw'ikwirakwira ry'indwara kandi ryatangajwe muri The Journal of Travel Medicine hagati ya Mutarama 2020.
Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu bya mbere byagize ingendo nyinshi zivuye i Wuhan, hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu 2018 yavuye mu Muryango Mpuzamahanga w'Ubwikorezi bw'Ikirere.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe nk'ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abashoramari baturutse i Wuhan.
Benshi mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane muri Aziya, Bali ni yo yavuzwe ko idashobora gukora cyane mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Australia ari yo yavuzwe ko ishobora gukora cyane. Australia yatangaje gahunda yo gusubiza mu bihe bidasanzwe ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare kubera Novel Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Byatangajwe ko hari byinshi bigikenewe kumenyekana kuri COVID-19 kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no kuvugana mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habayeho ikibazo cy'umutekano muke mu buzima bw'abantu.
Kubera ko ingendo z'abantu n'ibintu by'ibanze mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei byamaze igihe byamaze guhagarikwa, ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gutegura ko abaturage n'abakozi ba ambasade babyo bava muri ako gace, mbere na mbere babifashijwemo n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa, binyuze mu ndege zafatiriwe n'ibihugu byabo.
Mu bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gutegura gucyura abaturage babyo harimo Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Australia, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand.
Pakistan yatangaje ko itazongera gucyura abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yakuye muri icyo gihugu abaturage b'abanya-Burezili 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'abanya-Polonye bane, Umushina umwe n'Umuhinde.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bari bahagaze muri Polonye aho indege yavuye muri Bresil yafashe intera mbere yo kujya muri Bresil.
Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 barokowe (abantu 176 bari mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari ifite icyangombwa na Leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB i Trenton, maze bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege y'Abanyakanada 185 yavuye i Wuhan ijya i Trenton muri CFB.
Abategetsi ba Australia bakuye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, babashyira mu kigo cyo gufungirwa ku kirwa cya Noheli, cyakoreshejwe mu buryo bushya nk'ahantu ho gushyirwa mu kato, maze bamarayo iminsi 14.
Indege y'abimukira ivuye muri Nouvelle Zelande yageze muri Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe baturutse muri Australia na Pacifique) bari bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'ingabo z'igihugu i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gutabara Abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess Proud.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege itwara abagenzi yari itwaye Abanyakanada 129 yavuye i Diamond Princess igera i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, Guverinoma y'u Buhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage b'u Buhinde muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yakiriwe na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yazanye abaturage 112 b'Abanyafurika y'Epfo.
Mbere yo kugenda, abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus, bari barafashwe kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago byo kwandura.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragayeho ubwandu bwa coronavirus, nibo bonyine bahawe ubuhungiro.
Ibizamini byagarutse ku baturage bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, barimo abakozi ba ndege, abashoferi, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, bakekwaho ibikorwa by'ubutabazi, kandi abandi bose bashyizwe mu kato k'iminsi 14 mu kigo cya Ranch Resort nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Irani kubera icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byoherereje ubufasha Ubushinwa.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri b'Abashinwa bateraniye muri Kaminuza ya Amerika bagiye kohereza imfashanyo mu duce twugarijwe na virusi mu Bushinwa. Itsinda rimwe ryo mu karere ka Chicago rifatanyije na bo ryatumye udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu karere ka Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubufasha bw'ubumuntu wafatanyije na Direct Relief Fedex wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite birimo utwenda, imyenda, ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku ya 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya WHO mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'ibikorwa byo kuruvura, ndetse no kurinda "abantu bafite ibyago byinshi muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaction yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon ageze udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga y'amadolari y'Amerika miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko izatangaza inkunga ya miliyoni 18 z'amaboko y'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye birimo amasuti 10,000 ya Hazmat, na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi zisezeranya inkunga y'inyongera ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu bihugu byazahajwe.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu Butaliyani kugira ngo bifashe guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 muri Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 na udupfukamunwa 60,000 byo gukingira kugira ngo tujye gutangwa mu Muryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yaho yohereje muri Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na ventilateri 5.
Mama kandi yatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada, agaragaza amakenga ku masike n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'abaturutse mu Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Czech DRC.
Urugero, Espagne yataye mu bikorwa ibikoresho 58,000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa bifite igipimo cy'ubuziranenge cya 30% gusa, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwasubije udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'Abashinwa twari dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwasubije mu gihugu udupfukamunwa 100,000 tutakoreshwa, twitwaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, ingamba z'Ubushinwa zarakiriwe neza mu bice bitandukanye bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yemeye gahunda y'ubufasha bw'ibanze ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye imbaraga z'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
OMS yagaragaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002/ 2004, aho abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga kubungabunga ibanga ryabangamiye ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kugenzura, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu, aho leta nkuru ya leta itanga amakuru buri gihe kugirango ihagarike ubwoba mbere y'ibiruhuko by'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu rwego rwo gusubiza icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bwo hagati cyo gushyiraho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS, Goden Gally, yagize ati ""WHO ntabwo byanze bikunze yatugiriye inama"", kandi ni "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cyo kwiyemeza guhashya icyorezo ku isi hose aho cyagwiriye cyane", avuga ko ari ""igitangaza mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange"". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma y'uko abantu bo hanze y'u Bushinwa bemeje ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu no kongera umubare w'ibyabaye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubuzima rusange gihangayikishije (Public Health Emergency of International Concern, PICHE), nyuma ya PICHE ya mbere kuva mu 2009 ubwo yatangazaga icyorezo cy'ibicurane ku isi hose.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko PHEIC yatewe n'uko "ibihugu bifite amikoro make n'ibifite ubukungu buciriritse, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza, bishobora kugira ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira ku isi".
Mu gusubiza ku ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'ibihano ku ngendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zibuza ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi bidafite akamaro", yongeraho ko "WHO idashishikariza guhagarika ubucuruzi n'ibikorwa".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo kwitegura mu buryo bw'ibanze mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko hari n'ubufasha bw'ibanze buhabwa ibihugu bifite "uburyo bwo kumenya abantu bahuye n'iyi virusi mu karere kabyo, kabone n'iyo yaba yaramaze kwandura".
"Tedros yakomeje atangaza ko "" dukomeye nk'aho dufite imbaraga z'urusobe rw'ibinyabuzima " " kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga" gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura nyuma. " Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yatangije izina rya COVID-19 mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru.
"Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye "gutanga imbaraga z'uburyo bwose bwa Loni mu gusubiza".
"Ibi byatumye itsinda ry'ubuyobozi bw'ibiza rya ONU rikora, ryemerera amahanga yose guhuza ibisubizo by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, ibyo WHO ivuga ko bizatuma "bitangira kwita ku bisubizo by'ubuzima, kandi izindi nzego zikoresha ubushobozi bwazo mu guhangana n'ingaruka zikomeye z'imibereho, ubukungu n'iterambere by'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'ibikorwa ryifatanyije riyobowe na WHO ryakoze hamwe n'u Bushinwa kugira ngo rizane itsinda ry'abahanga mpuzamahanga na WHO ku butaka bw'Ubushinwa kugira ngo bafashe mu gucunga mu gihugu no gusuzuma ubukana n'ubushobozi bwo kwanduza iki cyorezo binyuze mu mahugurwa n'inama n'ibigo by'ibanze bitandukanye by'igihugu, kandi bagende mu turere dukwiriye kugira ngo barebe ingaruka n'ibisubizo by'ibikorwa ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu.Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ko isi irimo kwitegura kurushaho iki cyorezo cya coronavirus, ivuga ko nubwo kititiriwe kivugwa ko ari icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kwitegura.
"Mu gusubiza icyorezo cya Iran, OMS yoherejeyo itsinda ryabo kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ku mugaragaro ko icyiciro cy'ibyago byo kwandura coronavirus ku isi kizazamurwa kiva ku cyiciro cya ""cyinshi"" kijya ku cyiciro cya ""cyinshi cyane"", kikaba ari cyo cyiciro cyo hejuru cy'ubuziranenge n'ibyago".
"Mike Ryan, umuyobozi w'ishami rya WHO rishinzwe ibibazo by'ingutu by'ubuzima, mu itangazo yatanze, yaburiye ko ""ibi ari ikigeragezo gikomeye kuri buri butegetsi ku isi: mukanguke".
"Uyu mugera ushobora kuba uri hafi kandi ugomba kwitegura", uburyo bwiza bwo kubyifatamo bushobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi cyane kurusha ibindi".
"Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adatanga ibimenyetso by'uko abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange bashobora gutangaza ko ari icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo bivuze ko ""tuzi neza ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyi virusi""".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi w'ubuyobozi yavuze ko OMS "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ubwiyongere bw'iki cyorezo n'imiterere y'ubudehe bwayo. OMS yahuye n'ibitotezo byinshi kubera uburyo buke bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza ibyihutirwa by'ubuzima rusange no gutinda gushyiraho icyorezo".
Mu bitangazwaho nabi harimo n'icyifuzo cyo kwegura kwa Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 kugeza ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zigera kuri 12 zasobanuye akamaro ko kubahiriza uburenganzira bwa buri muntu muri iki gihe cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ibyo akora birokora ubuzima kandi ko Leta ari inshingano zayo.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bidashobora kuba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni itsinda runaka.
Abahanga bemeje ko abafite ubumuga, abanyamuryango b'imitwe mito, abageze mu za bukuru, abatagira aho baba, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bantu batagira aho babogamiye bakeneye ubufasha bwa Leta bose bafite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga birimo kwibanda ku ngaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage z'ikibazo cya COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubukungu n'Iterambere watangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ku gihe no ku buryo bwimbitse ku bitekerezo by'ingamba ibihugu byo ku isi bifata, ndetse no gutanga ibitekerezo n'inama.
Ubukungu bwisi burimo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'ingamba zo gukomeza uburyo bwo kwivuza, ingendo, ibigo bya digitale n'ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga, kandi bigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku bindi no koroshya imikoranire ku isi mu guhangana n'imbogamizi z'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Guverinoma ya Amerika, Minisitiri w'Abongereza ushinzwe ibiro bya Kabine Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Jair Bolsonaro, Eduardo Bolsonaro banenze guverinoma y'Ubushinwa ku buryo yakemuye icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi bo mu nzego z'ibanze z'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) birukanywe ku mirimo yabo kubera ko bagerageje gushyira abantu mu kato mu bice byo hagati mu Bushinwa, bigaragara ko byerekana ko batishimiye amashyirahamwe ya politiki yibanda ku cyorezo muri ibyo bice.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko iki gikorwa cyafashwe mu rwego rwo kurinda Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage bwatewe n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, bahakana ibinyoma by'uko COVID-19 yavuye muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani, bahakana ibyatangajwe mbere ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiriye i Wuhan.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump bwa Amerika bwise coronavirus "Virus y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan", buvuga ko Ubushinwa "bwatangiye gukumira virusi ubu imaze kuba icyorezo ku isi", ibisubizo bya bamwe mu bayivuguruza bivuga ko ari amacakubiri kandi "ni ugushaka kuyobya abantu ku kuntu ubutegetsi bwayo bwananiwe gukumira iki cyorezo".
"The Daily Beast yavuze ku mikorere ya Leta ya Amerika isobanura uburyo bwo kuvugana n'ibitangazamakuru by'ibanze ku Kanama k'Umutekano w'Igihugu, aho iyo nzira yavuzwe ko ari "ibintu byose bijyanye n'Ubushinwa".
"Turasabwa kugerageza gukwirakwiza ubwo butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama n'amateraniro y'abanyamakuru no kugaragara kuri televiziyo". "Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari igice cy'igikorwa cyo gukwirakwiza imbaraga ku isi".
"Joseph Borel, umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga y'ubumwe bw'uburayi, yaburiye ko hari "igice cya gipolitiki-mpuzamahanga kirimo no guhimba inkuru no guharanira kugira ingaruka binyuze muri 'politiki y'ubwisanzure'".
"Borrell yakomeje avuga ko ""Ubushinwa buri gushyiraho ubutumwa bukomeye ko bitandukanye na Amerika, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe""".
Ubushinwa bwasabye Amerika kenshi guhagarika inkunga yabwo muri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, nyuma y'aho byamenyekanye ko bwohereje imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu bibiri bya nyuma.
Imfashanyo y'udupfukamunwa 100,000 Jack Ma yahaye Cuba yahagaritswe ku ya 3 Mata n'ibihano bya Amerika.
Abategetsi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bashinjwa gukoresha imfashanyo bahaga ibindi bihugu mu nyungu z'igihugu cyabo.
Ibihugu by'u Budage, Autriche n'Ubusuwisi, n'ibindi nka Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani, byagize amakimbirane ku bijyanye n'imisatsi.
Turukiya kandi yafashe udupupe tw'umwuka amagana twari twashyizwe muri Espagne.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze ko EU idafite ubumwe mu guhangana n'Ubutaliyani bwugarijwe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwashubije mu buryo bw'impande zombi".
"Nibyo rwose ntabwo ari ikimenyetso cyiza ku bumwe bw'u Burayi".
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte kuri telefoni, Perezida Vladimir Putin w'u Burusiya yategetse ingabo z'u Burusiya kohereza mu Butaliyani abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka z'ubumara bwihariye n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
"Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa cyanditse ku izina ry'umuntu utazwi "imiterere ikomeye ya politiki" kivuga ko 80% by'ubufasha bw'Uburusiya "bwari nta cyo bumaze cyangwa nta kamaro bufitiye Ubutaliyani".
"Uru rubuga rwamushinje ko ari mu gikorwa cyo gushimisha u Burusiya "mu buryo bwa gipolitiki n'ubw'ubumenyingiro".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, n'umushikiranganji w'ububanyi n'amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi de Mayo, banze ibyo bitangazamakuru bavuga kandi barashimira.
Uburusiya bwongeye kohereza indege y'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "iyo bigeze ku gufasha bagenzi be bo muri Amerika, [Putin] atekereza ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bo muri Amerika bazaba bafite imbaraga, na bo bashobora kuzishyura".
"Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO ""Defender 2020"" iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, izaba ari imyitozo ikomeye ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubukonje irangiye, izaba ku kigero cyagabanutse".
Kate Hudson, umunyamabanga mukuru wa The Campaign for Nuclear Disarmament, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho, ntabwo bizashyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'ingabo z'Amerika n'ibindi bihugu byinshi by'iburayi, ahubwo bizashyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bigenzura".
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yanditse ibaruwa ifunguye ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe 2020 asaba abayobozi b'isi ubufasha, avuga ko Amerika ikomeje gufatira ibihano Iran, bituma kurwanya iki cyorezo bigorana kubera ko igihugu cye gifite amahirwe make yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga.
Abasesengura politiki bavuze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida yo mu 2020. Imibanire ya diplomasi hagati y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo yangiritse mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'isi.
"Nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangarije ko buri muntu wese uvuye muri Koreya y'Epfo agomba gushyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu gace kagenwe na leta, Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'Ubuyapani yo gushyira mu kato idafite ishingiro kandi idafite imbaraga".
Mu mizo ya mbere, umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo wari mu nzira ebyiri zitandukanye mu buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye icyo kibazo.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku kirego basaba ko Moon yirukanwa, basaba ko leta itera iki cyorezo nabi, abandi benshi bashyize umukono ku kirego bashimira igisubizo cye. Icyorezo cy'isi cyatumye ibihugu byinshi byashyiraho amategeko y'ibihe bidasanzwe mu rwego rwo guhangana nacyo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko bafite impungenge ko ibyo bishobora gutuma leta ikomeza gushimangira ububasha bwayo.
Muri Hongiriya, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko iha Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orban ububasha bwo gutangaza iteka ryo kuyobora igihugu igihe kitaragera, gusubika Inteko Ishinga Amategeko cyangwa kuyobora amatora no guhana abantu b'ibyamamare batangaza amakuru atari yo ku bijyanye n'uko iki cyorezo cyandura ndetse n'uburyo leta ikemura iki kibazo.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatewe n'ibura ry'ibicuruzwa, kwiyongera kw'ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho by'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo, gutera ubwoba no guhungabanya ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'uko abakiriya bifuza cyane kandi abaguzi bakaba batabasha kubikora.
Mu bice byinshi, abantu bagurishije ibiribwa byinshi, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi mu tubati, bituma habaho ubukene mu gutanga ibicuruzwa.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu buryo bwihariye cyatanze umuburo ku bijyanye no gutinda kohereza ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki.
Dukurikije uko umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, abifuza ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo, biyongereyeho inshuro 100.
Ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa by'imiti byongereweho inshuro 20 kandi byateje ibyumweru bitandatu by'izamuka ry'ibicuruzwa.
Byatumye ku isi hose habaho ubukene bw'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kandi OMS yaburiye ko byashyira mu kaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Icyorezo muri Australia cyatumye abacuruzi ba Daegu babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Australia mu Bushinwa.
Iki gikorwa cyatumye ibiribwa by'abana bidahagije mu maduka manini, kandi nyuma yaho leta ya Australia yatangaje ko bibujijwe. Nubwo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan habayeho ikwirakwira ry'ibyago byinshi bya COVID-19, byemeje ko hari ibyifuzo byinshi by'ibiribwa, uturere twombi twitandukanyije n'ibura ry'ibiribwa mu buryo bukomeye.
Ingamba zafashwe n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo gukingira no kurwanya ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko bw'ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi zagize icyo zigeraho, bituma hatabaho ibura ry'ibiribwa mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru nk'uko byari byitezwe.
Nubwo ibicuruzwa by'ubuhinzi byo mu majyaruguru y'Ubutaliyani bitigeze bigabanuka cyane, ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko bivugwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Mu gihe abayobozi ba leta y'Ubushinwa barekuye inyama z'ingurube zari zitezwe mu bubiko kugira ngo abaturage babone ibyo kurya bihagije, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, babanje guhura n'ibikoresho bidafite aho bifatira.
Ubutaliyani bufite amategeko nk'ayo asaba abahinzi kubika ibiribwa mu gihe cy'ibiza.
Ubushinwa nabwo bwagize ingaruka ku bukungu bw'isi: Nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku ya 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 bitewe n'ingamba zafashwe na leta zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwagabanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa bukomeye ariwo murwa w'ingenzi mu bukungu n'inganda, icyorezo cy'iyi virusi gishobora guteza ihungabana rikomeye mu bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu cya Economist Intelligence Unit, ateganya ko amasoko azakomeza guhindagurika kugeza igihe habonetse ishusho isobanutse neza y'ibishobora kubaho.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu by'inganda batangaje ko ubukungu bw'isi buzahinduka bukazamuka cyane kurusha icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Impuguke yo muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis, igaragaza ko ibihombo byo mu rwego rw'isi mu bijyanye n'itangwa ry'ibiribwa bishobora kugera kuri miliyari 300 z'amadolari, bishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
"Opec" ngo "yarasenyutse" nyuma y'uko ibiciro by'ibikomoka kuri peteroli byagabanutse cyane kubera ko hari ibisabwa bike ku Bushinwa.
Ku ya 24 Gashyantare, amasoko y'imigabane ku isi yose yaguye kubera ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa wariyongereye cyane.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, kubera impungenge zikomeje kwiyongera ku cyorezo cya coronavirus, imibare myinshi y'ibicuruzwa bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, harimo NASDAQ-100, S&P 500 Index na Dow Jones Industrial Average, byatangaje ko byaguye cyane kuva mu 2008, Dow igeze ku manota 1.191, ari nayo ya mbere yagabanutse cyane mu munsi umwe kuva mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'imari mu 2007-08.
Ibipimo uko ari bitatu byazamutseho 10% mu mpera z'icyumweru.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Scope Ratings GmbH yemeje indangamuntu y'ubusugire bw'Ubushinwa, ariko ikomeza kugira isura mbi.
Ibiciro by'imigabane byongeye kugabanuka kubera ubwoba bwa coronavirus, ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, ku gipimo cyo hasi cyane.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu bw'isi bugiye guhungabana.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu, Mohamed El-Erian, yashimye uburyo Banki Nkuru n'igihugu byafashe ingamba mu gihe cy'ibiza.
Banki nkuru z'ibihugu zirimo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubukungu mu buryo bwihuse kurusha uko byagenze mu 2008.
Ubucuruzi ni kimwe mu bigo byibasiwe cyane n'ibihano bya leta ku byerekeye ingendo, ahantu hose hari abaturage benshi, harimo n'ahantu nyaburanga ho gutemberera, ndetse no ku ngendo zose ku isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko ingendo z'indege nyinshi zirimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas zitaragenze neza kubera ko hari abantu bake cyane bari babikeneye, bitewe n'uko Flybe, ikigo cy'indege cyo mu Bwongereza, cyarasenyutse.
Ingaruka mbi cyane ku isosiyete y'ubukerarugendo ntizari zigeze ziboneka mbere.
Ibibuga byinshi by'indege n'ibibuga by'amato na byo byafunzwe.
Igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa ni cyo cy'ingenzi mu bihe by'ubukerarugendo mu Bushinwa, igihe icyorezo cyatangiriye mu Bushinwa.
Ibihe byinshi bishobora kuba birimo abantu benshi, nk'ibirori ngarukamwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, byahagaritswe na guverinoma y'igihugu n'intara.
Ibirori byinshi byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'ukwezi n'ibitaramo by'ingenzi birimo ibirori by'umugi wabujijwe n'urusengero rw'umwimerere byahagaritswe mu mujyi wa Beijing mu rwego rwo kwirinda abantu benshi.
Abategetsi mu ntara 24, mu mirenge 31 n'uturere tw'u Bushinwa, bongereye ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko imirimo myinshi itazongera gufungurwa kugeza kuri iyo tariki.
