Ibizamini bya laboratwari by'indwara ya coronavirus y'ubuhumekero 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi ifitanye isano na SARS-CoV-2 birimo uburyo bwo gutahura ko virusi iriho no kumenya ko hari abanduye.
Kuba virusi iri mu bipimo byemezwa na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Iki kizamini ni cyihariye kandi kigamije gutahura RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 gusa.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ko hari ubwandu buherutse cyangwa bukomeje.
Igishushanyo cy'umubiri (serologie) gishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abantu banduye, harimo n'abantu bafite ibimenyetso bike cyane byo gutangaza cyangwa badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibizamini byakozwe n'iki kigo, byerekana umubare nyawo w'abahitanwa n'iki cyorezo ndetse n'ubushobozi bw'abantu bwo kwirinda iki cyorezo.
Kubera ibizamini bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku byorezo bya virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3%, kandi umubare w'abageragejwe mu bihugu bitandukanye waratandukanye cyane.
Ibi bishobora kugira ingaruka ku mibare y'abapfa mu barwayi, mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bikaba bishobora kuba birenze urugero.
Ibipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe hakoreshejwe uburyo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo bya nasopharyngeal swabs cyangwa ibipimo by'amacandwe, bishobora gupimwa hifashishijwe uburyo bwa Real-Time Reverse Transcription Polymerase Chain Reaction (rRT-PCR).
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Igikorwa cya RT-PCR cyakozwe hakoreshejwe ibipimo byo mu muhogo ni cyo cyonyine cyizewe mu byumweru bya mbere by'indwara.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kuva mu muhogo, ariko ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye, mu cyumweru cya kabiri cyo gusuzumwa, ibindi bishobora gukoreshwa nyuma yo gufata ibipimo mu mwuka, cyangwa ibintu byasohotse hamwe no gukorora (umuhogo).
Imwe mu ngamba za mbere za PCR yatangijwe muri Mutarama 2020 i Charité i Berlin, ikoresheje uburyo bwa Real-Time Reverse Transcription Polymerase Chain Reaction (rRT-PCR), kandi yashyizeho urufatiro rw'ibikoresho 250,000 bizatangwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO).
Ubwongereza nabwo bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Isosiyete yo muri Koreya y'Epfo Kogenebiotech yakoze ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cya PCR gishingiye kuri SARS-CoV-2 cyo gupima (PowerChek Coronavirus) ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
"Iri shami rishinzwe ubushakashatsi rirashaka gusanga ubwoko busanzwe bwa ""E"" muri koronavirusi zose za beta na RdRp, ubwoko bw'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2. BGI Group mu Bushinwa ni imwe mu bigo bya mbere byahawe uruhushya rwo gukoresha mu buryo bwihutirwa igikoresho cy'ubushakashatsi cya SARS-CoV-2 gishingiye kuri PCR n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Ibikoresho by'Ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa. Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (CDC) kirimo gutanga RT-PCR panel ku bigo nderabuzima by'ubuzima rusange mu gihe cy'igihe cya 2019-novel coronavirus (2019-nCoV) binyuze mu bikoresho mpuzamahanga by'ibanze".
Ibisubizo bitarasobanutse byatewe n'ibipimo bitatu bya kera by'ibikoresho by'ibizamini byatewe n'ibipimo byagenewe kimwe mu bikoresho by'ibizamini kandi bigatuma ibizamini bibangamira CDC i Atlanta; byatumye ingero nkeya ku munsi zigera ku 100 zikorwa neza muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri ntibyemejwe ko ari ibyiringirwa kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, kandi kugeza icyo gihe, ibigo by'ibanze na leta ntibyemerewe gutangira gukora ibizamini.
Iki cyemezo cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (Food and Drug Administration) mu gihe cy'ikoreshwa ry'ibipimo byihutirwa. Ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyo muri Amerika cyatangiye gukora ibizamini mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko hari gukorwa ibizamini bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR mu gihugu hose.
Quest Diagnostics nayo yatangije ibizamini bya COVID-19 ku rwego rw'igihugu ku ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta gihagararo cy'ubwinshi cyatangajwe; ibipimo bigomba gukusanywa no gutunganywa nk'uko bisabwa na CDC.
Ikigo cya Leta cy'Ubushakashatsi mu by'Ubwanduzi n'Ikoranabuhanga mu Binyabuzima, VECTOR, ni cyo cyateguye kandi cyakora ikizamini cya COVID-19 mu Burusiya.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe na Federal Service for Surveillance in Healthcare. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, habonetse raporo y'uko Mayo Clinic yari ikoze ikizamini cyo gutahura ubwandu bwa COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha arenga 3.5, bityo yemerera igikoresho gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4,128 mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye Abbott Laboratories uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) rwo gukora igerageza kuri Abbott's m2000 system; FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo ku Hologic, LabCorp, na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid yahawe EUA na FDA kugira ngo ikore isuzuma, ryamaze iminota 45.
FDA yemeje ikigo cy'ubuvuzi gikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongerera ingufu za nucleic acid (ACA) mu mwanya wa PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ingendo z'ubushyuhe, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu minota itanu cyangwa se ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Kugeza ubu, muri Amerika hari ibikoresho bigera ku 18,000, kandi Abbott irateganya kongera umusaruro kugira ngo ishobore gutanga ibizamini 50,000 ku munsi. Ikigeragezo kimwe gikoresha umubiri umwe wa monoclonal, gifatanya by'umwihariko na poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (N protein) ya coronavirus nshya, kandi kiri gukorwa muri Tayiwani mu byiringiro by'uko gishobora gutanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko bigenda ku bipimo bya rubagimpande.
"Inyigo y'ibitabo yo muri Werurwe 2020 yafashe umwanzuro w'uko ""gushushanya mu gatuza mu byiciro bya mbere nta gaciro bifite mu gusuzuma indwara, ariko amakuru aturuka kuri CT [computed tomography] ashobora kuba ahari mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira""".
Mu bintu CT ifite harimo impande ebyiri, impande nyinshi z'ibirahuri by'ibirahuri bifite impande, impande zitari zisanzwe n'iz'inyuma.
Iyo indwara igitangira, habaho ubwigenge bwo mu mutwe, ubuhumyi no gukomera.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranya PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho icyorezo cy'iki gihe cyatangiriye, bwagaragaje ko CT irusha cyane PCR ubushobozi bwo kumva, ariko ko idasobanutse neza, kandi ko ibintu byinshi byerekana ko ifata amashusho bihuye n'ibindi bibazo bya nimoniya n'izindi ndwara.
"Muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imirase cyatanze inama ko ""CT itagomba gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cya mbere cyo gupima cyangwa gusuzuma COVID-19". Muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yatanze inama yo gukoresha PCR mu gupima kwa mbere".
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'umubiri ku cyorezo ni ugukora za 'antibodies' zirimo IgM na IgG.
Zishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ubwandu mu bantu, mu gupima ubudahangarwa no kugenzura abaturage guhera ku minsi 7 y'ibimenyetso. Iperereza ryakorwa na laboratwari nkuru (CLT) n'ibipimo byo ku rwego rwo kwita ku bantu (PoCT).
Ibigo byinshi by'ibanze bizakoresha uburyo bwikora neza cyane muri laboratwari, ariko kuboneka kwabo bizaterwa n'ibipimo by'umusaruro kuri buri buryo.
Icyitegererezo kimwe cy'amaraso y'uruhande rw'umubiri ni cyo gikoreshwa cyane muri CLT, nubwo ibipimo by'urukurikirane bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukurikirana ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara.
