"Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe mu kigo bwagaragaje ko nibura ibipimo 483,295 byageragejwe kugeza ku cyumweru cya 12/2020 kugeza no ku wa 12/2020, kandi ibipimo 33,491 (6.9%) byemejwe ko byanduye SARS-CoV-2. Abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam muri Israel bakoze uburyo bwo gupima ibipimo hamwe by'abarwayi 64 hamwe, hanyuma bagakora ibindi bipimo gusa iyo ibipimo byakozwe byemejwe ko byanduye.
Ibikorwa byakozwe na Wang Jian washinze BGI, byakozwe mu minsi itanu, byerekana ko iyo ibizamini bitongera gukorwa mu gihe gikwiriye, umubare w'abanduye muri Hubei wari kuba wiyongereyeho 47% kandi ibiciro byo guhangana n'igikorwa cyo gushyirwa mu kato byari kuzikuba kabiri.
