Mu kwezi kwa Werurwe, ibura ry'imiti n'ibura ry'imiti byabaye inzitizi mu gupima abantu benshi mu Burayi, mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika.
Ibi byatumye abashakashatsi bamwe na bamwe bagenzura uburyo bwo gutegura ibipimo aho ibipimo byashyushye iminota 5 ku 98 °C (208 °F) kugirango bifungure genomes za RNA kugirango zigezweho. Ku ya 31 Werurwe byatangajwe ko UAE ubu irimo gupima abantu benshi kuri coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu cyose kandi iri mu nzira yo kongera ibipimo kugirango igere ku gice kinini cy'abaturage.
"Byakorewe mu guhuza ubushobozi bwo gutwara no kugura laboratwari y'ikoranabuhanga ry'ikoranabuhanga mu rwego rw'abaturage (ishingiye ku bigo by'ubushakashatsi byitwa "Huo-Yan" byo mu Bushinwa) biturutse kuri Group 42 na BGI".
Iki kigo cyubatswe mu minsi 14 gifite ubushobozi bwo gukora ibizamini bya RT-PCR inshuro ibihumbi 10 ku munsi, kikaba ari cyo cya mbere ku isi gikora hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ibipimo bitandukanye byakozwe mu Bushinwa, Ubufaransa, Ubudage, Hong Kong, Ubuyapani na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika bigamije kureba ibice bitandukanye by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bya coronavirus.
Ubudage bwashyize mu bikorwa uburyo bwo gukora ibikoresho byo kohereza mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, bitagira ubushobozi bwo gukora ibikoresho byabyo bwite, byemejwe na OMS.
Uburyo bw'ubudage bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku ya 17 Mutarama 2020; porogaramu yateguwe n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara ntiyabonekaga kugeza ku ya 28 Mutarama, bituma ibizamini biboneka muri Amerika bidatinze. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, Ubushinwa na Amerika byagize ibibazo ku kwizerwa kw'ibikoresho byo gupima, kandi ibyo bihugu na Ositaraliya ntibyashoboye gutanga ibikoresho bihagije byo gukemura ibyifuzo no gutanga inama zo gupimwa n'inzobere mu by'ubuzima.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, impuguke zivuga ko gupima cyane muri Koreya y'Epfo byafashije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya coronavirus.
Ubutegetsi bwa Koreya y'Epfo bumaze imyaka myinshi bwubaka ubushobozi bwo gupima mu bigo by'ubushakashatsi byigenga.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye ko gahunda yo gupima yongerwa nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo cya COVID-19.Icyorezo cy'indwara cyatumye hakenerwa cyane ibizamini, bituma laboratwari z'abikorera muri Amerika zitangira gukora ibizamini bibarirwa muri za miriyoni, kandi bituma habaho ikibazo cyo kubura swab n'ibikoresho by'imiti.
Mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari ibibazo by'ubuziranenge mu bikoresho byayo by'isuzuma.
