Gukaraba intoki (cyangwa gukaraba intoki), nanone bizwi nka isuku y'intoki, byerekeza ku gusukura intoki z'umuntu mu rwego rwo gukuraho ibitaka, amavuta, mikorobe cyangwa ibindi bintu bidakenewe.
"Gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabuni mu "bihe bikomeye" by'umunsi, bifasha kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibiheri na kolera, zandurira mu binyoma no mu kanwa".
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa imbeho isanzwe, urugero, niba badakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa (ni ukuvuga mu muhogo).
Ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi by'umunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa ni: mbere na nyuma yo gusama, nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura utwenda tw'imbere, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no gutegura amafunguro cyangwa guteka inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Iyo nta mazi n'isabune bihari, bashobora gukaraba intoki bakoresheje imyanda.
Mbere yo guteka, mu gihe cyo guteka na nyuma yo guteka.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura indimu cyangwa se nyuma yo gusukura icyumba cy'abana.
Nyuma yo gukorora, gukorora cyangwa kwitsamura.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, ibiryo by'amatungo, cyangwa imyanda y'amatungo.
Isuku y'amaboko mu buvuzi ni ingeso nziza mu buvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gutanga imiti cyangwa kwitabwaho n'abaganga bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Impamvu y'ibanze yo gukaraba intoki mu buvuzi ni ugukuraho mikorobe (indwara, virusi, cyangwa ibindi binyabuzima bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'imiti bishobora kwangiza cyangwa guteza indwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bita ku biribwa cyangwa bakora mu buvuzi, ariko ni ingenzi no ku bantu muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini ku buzima, harimo kugabanya ubwandu bw'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zitandura; gukumira indwara zandura ziterwa n'ibiheri; kugabanya ubwandu bw'ibicurane byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero;
no kugabanya impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo zabo.
Ubushakashatsi bwo mu mwaka wa 2013 bwagaragaje ko imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki ishobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu batagira uburebure.
Mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iziterwa n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka mu gihe hakozwe impinduka zoroheje mu myitwarire, nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Iyi gahunda yoroshye ishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa kubera iyi ndwara ku kigero cya 50%.
Ingamba zo gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki zishobora kugabanya igipimo cy'indwara y'umwijima ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, kandi ibyo ni nk'ibigereranywa no gutanga amazi meza mu duce dukennye.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabuni bifitanye isano no kugabanya indwara y'ibiheri ku kigero cya 48%. Uburyo bumwe rukumbi kandi bw'ingirakamaro kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda ibicurane n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARI) ni ugukaraba intoki n'isabuni nk'umuco wisanzuye mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Imyotsi y'ibihaha, ari nayo mpamvu nyamukuru itera indwara y'ibihaha, ni yo mpamvu nyamukuru y'urupfu mu bana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu.
Indwara y'igifu n'imyuka itera indwara y'ibicurane ni zimwe mu mpamvu zihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko guhindurira abantu akamenyero ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero bishobora kurokora ubuzima kurusha urukingo cyangwa imiti, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri urupfu ruterwa n'indwara y'ibisebe, ndetse bikagabanya kimwe cya kane urupfu ruterwa n'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki bihuzwa n'ubundi buryo bwo kwiyuhagira nk'igice cy'ibikorwa by'amazi, isuku n'isuku (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki birinda indwara y'uruhu yandura ikwirakwira binyuze mu mikoranire y'abantu.
Ingaruka mbi zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma umubiri uhomba bitewe no kugira uruhu rwumye.
Ubushakashatsi bwo muri Danemark bwo mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera uburibwe, isura y'uruhu izwi nka eczema y'intoki cyangwa dermatite y'intoki, ibintu bikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakora mu by'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki kenshi cyane kandi ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero (OCD).
Ibihe bitanu byingenzi byumunsi aho gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ari ngombwa mu kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara z'imyanda ni: nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero (gusiramura, gusama), nyuma yo gusukura umwana cyangwa guhindura indimu, mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya no mbere/nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa gukorakora inyama, amafi cyangwa inkoko.
Mu bindi bihe byo gukaraba intoki neza mu kwirinda kwandura indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa igikomere; nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora, cyangwa gukaraba izuru; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukata inyamaswa; no gukorakora imyanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki ni muto cyane.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bihugu 54 mu 2015 bwagaragaje ko imiryango 38.7% ikoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabia Saoudite ifite igipimo kiri hejuru ku kigero cya 97%, Amerika iri hagati ya 77%, naho Ubushinwa bufite igipimo kiri hasi ku kigero cya 23%. Ubu hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire bwo kongera imikoreshereze yo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni mu bihe by'ibibazo.
"Gahunda y'ubwisungane mu kwivuza (Essential Health Care Program) ishyirwa mu bikorwa n'ishami ry'uburezi muri Filipine ni urugero rw'uburyo buhagije bwo guteza imbere ubuzima n'uburezi bw'abana".
Muri gahunda y'igihugu harimo kwivuza kabiri mu mwaka, gukaraba intoki buri munsi n'isabune, no gusukura amenyo buri munsi ukoresheje fluoride.
Ibi byakozwe neza muri Indonesia.
Kongeramo isabune cyangwa umuti w'isuku mu mazi bituma uruhu rukuraho mikorobe.
Imikorere y'ibikoresho by'isabune n'ibisuku ni ugugabanya ubuziranenge bw'umusemburo no kongera ubunyunyu.
Amazi yonyine nta cyo amaze kuko ibinure na poroteyine, ari byo bikomoka ku butaka, ntibishobora gukama mu mazi.
Mu by'ukuri, isuku iba ikorwa hifashishijwe amazi aciriritse.
Kubera ko isabune ya nitrate ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora gukomeza mikorobe ziterwa n'imikoreshereze y'ubundi buryo.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwibanze ku kwimura za bagiteri mu isabune idahumanye, bwerekanye ko kwimura byoroha kuko za bagiteri zihanagurwa n'ifuro.
"CDC iracyatangaza ko ""gukoresha isabune y'amazi ishobora gukoreshwa nta kuboko byasabwe""".
Hari amakuru menshi yatangajwe ku bantu bafite ubumenyi mu by'ubuzima ku bijyanye n'isabune z'imiti igabanya ubukana bwa mikorobe.
Kugeza ubu nta gihamya igaragaza ko hari umuti wica udukoko cyangwa umuti wica udukoko twica udukoko twanduye.
Ariko, isabune zica zabakiteri zirimo ibintu bisanzwe byabakiteri nka triclosan, bifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya ibifite ubuzima mu rugero rwagutse.
Bityo, nubwo udukoko turwanya imiti ngengabuzima tutatoranyijwe mu myambaro yica mikorobe, dushobora kuba tudakomeye nk'uko byamamazwa.
Usibye ibintu byo ku rwego rwo hejuru n'ibikoresho byo kurinda uruhu, imyiteguro ikorwa neza ishobora kuba irimo aside (acide acétique, ascorbic acid, acide lactique) nk'umugenzuzi wa pH, aside benzoïque ikora ku miti yica mikorobe, hamwe n'imiti y'uruhu y'inyongera (aloe vera, vitamine, menthol, ibimera). Isesengura ryuzuye ryakozwe n'ishuri ry'ubuzima rusange rya Oregon ryerekana ko isabune isanzwe nk'isabuni ya trichlosecane ifite anti-bakteri ikora neza mu kwirinda indwara no gukuraho mikorobe ku biganza.
Amazi ashyushye ahumuriza yo gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ku buryo yica mikorobe.
Bakteriya zikura vuba cyane ku bushyuhe bw'umubiri (37 °C).
Ariko amavuta kamere ni meza cyane mu gukuraho ubutaka n'udukoko tubufata kurusha amazi ashyushye n'isabune.
Ariko ibyo abahanga bavuga ko ari ibinyoma, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kunywa amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku mikorobe ziba mu biganza.
Isuku y'amaboko idashingiye ku mazi cyangwa umuti wica udukoko two mu ntoki utari ku mazi.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho by'isuku y'intoki bitagira alcohol (bizwi kandi nka rubs zishingiye ku nzoga, rubs z'intoki zanduza cyangwa sanitizer z'intoki) zitari zishingiye ku mazi zatangiye kwamamara.
Byinshi bikorerwa ku isopropyl alcohol cyangwa ethanol ikorwa hamwe na carbomers (polymers za acrylic acid) cyangwa humectants nk'imyanda mu mazi cyangwa ibintu byimbitse nka glycerine mu busa kugirango byorohereze gukoresha no kugabanya ingaruka zo kumesa inzoga.
Kongeramo imvange ya hydrogen-peroxide byongera ibikorwa bya antimicrobial. Amata y'isuku y'intoki afite byibuze 60 kugeza 95% by'inzoga zikora neza mu kwica mikorobe.
Alcohol rub sanitizers yica mikorobe, mikorobe zidakira imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), igituntu na virusi zimwe na zimwe (harimo HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, vaccine, influenza na hepatite) na fungus.
Alcohol rub sanitizer igizwe na 70% by'inzoga yica 99.97% (igabanuka rya log 3.5 ingana na 35 decibels) nyuma y'amasegonda 30 yo kuyikoresha ku ntoki, kandi yica 99.99% kugeza kuri 99.999% (4 kugeza kuri 5 igabanuka rya log 5) ya bagiteri nyuma y'umunota 1 yo kuyikoresha ku ntoki.
Amavuta yo gusukura intoki akoreshwa n'inzoga ni yo ahanini atuma indwara y'igifu idakira cyane, kandi nta cyo ageraho ku virusi ya Norovirus (cyangwa Norwalk). Gukoresha imiti yo gusukura intoki cyangwa gusukura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga nyinshi ni byiza.
Amavuta, ifu cyangwa gel, bikoreshwa mu kuboko kwombi imbere n'inyuma no hagati y'intoki kugeza igihe byumye, kandi ku mpera bigakoreshwa mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30.
Gukaraba intoki n'ibiganza byombi ni byiza. Ikigo cyo muri Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gitanga inama yo gukaraba intoki neza ukoresheje umuti wica udukoko, cyane cyane iyo wanduye.
Gukoresha ibyo bikoresho bigenda byiyongera bishingiye ku bworoheje bwo kubikoresha no guhitana vuba ibinyabuzima by'imikorere; nubwo, niba isabune n'amazi bidahari, ntibigomba gukoreshwa nk'isimbura ryo gukaraba intoki neza.
Iyo formula idafite imitsi n'/cyangwa umusemburo w'uruhu, gukoresha kenshi umuti wica intoki ukoreshwa n'inzoga bishobora gutera uruhu rwumye.
Ingaruka zo kumena inzoga zishobora kugabanuka cyangwa se zikarandurwa no kongeramo glycerine na / cyangwa andi mavuta mu buryo.
Mu igeragezwa mu buvuzi, imiti yo guhanagura intoki ikoreshwa n'inzoga irimo ibintu by'induhuro yatumye uruhu rudatera cyane kandi rukagira ubushyuhe budahagije ugereranyije n'isabune cyangwa umuti wica udukoko.
Indwara z'uruhu zituruka ku ndwara ziterwa n'isukari, indwara ziterwa n'isukari cyangwa kuba umuntu afite ikibazo cyo kumva inzoga cyangwa ibintu by'inzoga, si kenshi bijya bibaho mu gukaraba intoki.
Kugaragaza ko umuntu afite ibyago bike byo kurwara indwara z'uruhu bitewe no gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina, byaje kuba intandaro yo gukundwa n'abantu benshi ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabune.
Nubwo ari ingirakamaro, ibikoresho bidafite amazi ntibikora isuku y'intoki, ahubwo biyica gusa.
Kubera ko mikorobe zikomeza kuba ku biganza, kubera iyo mpamvu, isabune n'amazi ntibikora neza nko gukoresha imiti yo guhanagura intoki.
Imikorere y'imiti yo gukaraba intoki idafite inzoga ishingiye cyane ku bikoresho no ku buryo ikorwa, kandi mu bihe byashize, yakoze cyane ugereranyije n'imiti ikoreshwa n'inzoga na rubs.
Vuba aha cyane, abakoresha benzalkonium chloride bagaragaje ko ibikorwa bya antimicrobial bihamye kandi byiyongera nyuma yo gukoreshwa bitandukanye n'inzoga, bishoboka ko byatewe n'ibisubizo bibi by'uruhu bitewe no gukoreshwa kenshi.
Abantu benshi mu baturage batunze amafaranga make usanga badafite ubushobozi bwo kugura isabune, ahubwo bakoresha ivu cyangwa ibitaka.
Gusa ivu cyangwa ubutaka bishobora kuba byiza kurusha amazi ariko bishobora kuba bibi kurusha isabune.
Ikibazo cy'impungenge ni uko niba ubutaka cyangwa imyanda byandujwe na mikorobe bishobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira aho kugabanya.
Nk'uko bimeze ku isabune, ivu ni umuti wica udukoko kuko iyo rihuye n'amazi ritanga umuti wa alkaline.
Iyo isabune itaboneka, OMS itera inkunga isuku cyangwa umucanga nk'uburyo bwo gusimbuza isabune.
