"Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere aho amazi yo mu musarani na/cyangwa isabune idahari, uburyo butandukanye bw'igiciro gito bushobora gukorwa mu gukaraba intoki, urugero nko kuvoma amazi mu mazi anyura mu mazi cyangwa mu byatsi bifite imyobo ikwiriye, no/cyangwa gukoresha imyanda igihe bibaye ngombwa. Mu bihe aho amazi aba make (urugero mu mashuri cyangwa mu bice by'icyaro byo mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubika amazi nka ""TP-Tap"" n'ubundi buryo buhendutse".
