Mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo kurandura udukoko dutera indwara,
"Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi. Kongeramo imiti yica udukoko mu isabune ("isabuni" cyangwa "urwanya mikorobe") itanga ubushobozi bwo kwangiza ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki".
Ibi bikorwa byo kwica bishobora kuba mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa ahantu hari indwara z'ibicurane by'ibicurane. Kugira igikoresho cyo gukaraba intoki cyagombye kuba gifite aho gikora kandi kigakoreshwa nta gukorakora intoki, hari uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki bufite chlorhexidine cyangwa iodine, imiti yica udukoko twanduza ibicurane, n'udupira two gukaraba no gusukura munsi y'amanota.
Ibintu byose by'umurimbo bigomba gufungurwa.
Muri rusange, ubu buryo bukenera ko ukaraba intoki n'amavi mu gihe cy'iminota 2-6 (kugeza ku nkokora).
Gukaraba intoki igihe kirekire (iminota 10) si ngombwa.
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi ava mu rukenyerero kugera ku nkokora agomba kurindwa gusubira mu maboko.
Iyo bamaze gukaraba intoki, bagahanaguraho imyanda bakoresheje umwenda utanduye kandi bakambara ikanzu y'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo wirinde kwandura, ni byiza gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye cyangwa gukoresha imiti yica udukoko.
Mu rwego rwo kugenzura indwara z'ibicurane mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko inyungu nyinshi zo gukaraba intoki zabonetse mu gihe cyo gukaraba inshuro 20 ku ijana, kandi ko inyungu nke cyane zagaragaye igihe inshuro zo gukaraba intoki zariyongereye zigera hejuru ya 35 ku ijana.
