Ariko, isabune n'amazi/amazi ni ingirakamaro cyane kuruta rubs ishingiye ku nzoga mu kugabanya virusi ya H1N1 influenza A n'inkingo za Clostridium difficile ku biganza. Ibi bishobora kuba bikubiyemo gukaraba intoki, kwigisha abakozi ku bijyanye no kuboneka kwa rubs ishingiye ku nzoga, no kwibutsa abakozi mu nyandiko no mu magambo, mu guteza imbere isuku y'intoki mu nzego z'ubuzima.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi burakenewe ku kumenya niba izi mpinduka ari zo z'ingenzi cyane mu nzego z'ubuzima zitandukanye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabune byemewe ko ari uburyo buhendutse kandi bw'ingenzi bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, ndetse no kurya neza.
Icyakora, kubura amazi meza, isabune cyangwa uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abantu, mu mashuri no mu kazi, bituma kugera ku muco wo gukaraba intoki ku isi hose bigorana.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro bya Afurika, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo kubaka aho gukaraba intoki, usanga imifuka yo gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa buri muntu ku giti cye cyangwa bwa bose ari mike cyane.
Ariko kandi, umubare muto w'abantu bakaraba intoki ushobora kuba uturuka ku ngeso mbi cyane, aho kuba ari uko badafite isabune cyangwa amazi.
Gahunda yo gukaraba intoki n'isabune n'inama bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro y'itegeko, bikamenyekanisha ibyiza byo gukaraba intoki kandi bigatuma abantu bahindura ingeso zabo z'igihe kirekire.
Kugira ngo bigire icyo bigeraho, bigomba gukurikiranwa no gusuzumwa.
"Igenzura rya gahunda ry'ubushakashatsi 70 ryagaragaje ko ingamba zishingiye ku muryango zikora neza mu gukaraba intoki muri LMIC, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza ku mbuga nkoranyambaga bukora nabi. Urugero rw'ubukangurambaga ku gukaraba intoki mu mashuri ni "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF, itera amashuri inkunga yo gufata ingamba zoroshye, zifite ikiguzi gito kugira ngo abanyeshuri bakoreshe isabune mu gukaraba intoki, mu bindi bintu by'isuku".
Iyo amashuri ageze ku manota make, ashobora kugera ku nyenyeri eshatu.
Gushyiraho ibigo byo gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba kimwe mu bituma gahunda yo gukaraba intoki ikorwa mu rwego rwo kugabanya indwara n'imfu z'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu guhindura imyitwarire. Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF yashyizeho uburyo bwo kumenyekanisha imvugo yo gukaraba intoki.
DALYs zireba ubushakashatsi ku bijyanye no kwirinda, ku bijyanye no kugabanya ikiguzi cyo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ariko kandi, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune ari byo byoroshye kurusha ibindi bikoresho by'amazi n'isuku.
"Ingenzi yo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu  by'umwihariko ku bantu bari mu mimerere mibi, nk'ababyeyi bari mu bitaro baherutse kubyara cyangwa abasirikare bakomeretse - abapayiniya babiri b'isuku y'intoki babanje kubimenya mu kinyejana cya 19 rwagati: umuganga w'Umunyahungariya Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreraga i Vienne muri Autriche na Florence Nightingale, w'Icyongereza "washyizeho ubuvuzi bugezweho".
Kugeza icyo gihe, abantu benshi bemeraga ko indwara yatewe n'impumuro mbi y'ibinyampeke.
Mu myaka ya 1980, ibyorezo by'indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa hamwe n'indwara ziterwa n'ubuzima byatumye Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika Gishinzwe Kurwanya Indwara no Kuzihagarika gifasha cyane mu guteza imbere isuku y'intoki nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cya virusi itera SIDA cyateye mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020, byateje impagarara mu bihugu byinshi ku kamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
"Urugero, mu Budage, ibyapa birimo "ingamba nziza zo gukaraba intoki" byamanitswe mu bwiherero rusange no hafi y'ibikarabiro byo mu biro no ku bibuga by'indege".
"Iyi mvugo ngo "gukaraba intoki" isobanura ko umuntu yanga gufata inshingano cyangwa kuba umufasha w'icyaha".
Byaturutse mu gice cya Bibiliya cya Matayo aho Ponsiyo Pilato yavanye amaboko ku mwanzuro wo kubamba Yesu Kristo, ariko byatewe no gukoreshwa cyane mu baturage b'icyongereza, byabaye imvugo y'ururimi.
Muri Macbeth ya Shakespeare, Lady Macbeth atangira gukaraba intoki ze mu rwego rwo kugerageza gukuraho ibizinga by'ibitekerezo binyuze mu kugaragaza icyaha yakoze no gushishikariza umugabo we gukora ibyaha.
Byagaragaye kandi ko abantu, iyo batekereza cyangwa batekereza ku bikorwa by'ubwiyandarike, bakunze gukaraba intoki cyane kurusha abandi, kandi bakagura ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki cyane.
"Byongeye kandi, abantu bakaraba intoki nyuma y'iyo migambi ntibakunze gukora indi mirimo yo kwishyura" isuku "nk'uko bikorwa n'abakorerabushake".
