Gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukoresha ubwiherero ni itegeko mu idini rya Hindu, Abayahudi n'Abisilamu.
Kandi, gukaraba intoki mbere na nyuma yo kurya buri gihe ni itegeko mu idini rya Hindu, Buddhism, Sikhism, Yuda na Islam.
Gucunga ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 mu kazi
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa ingamba z'umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ingamba z'ibanze ku mikoreshereze myiza y'ibyago mu kazi ziterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'akazi akora, ibipimo by'ibyago by'ibitangazamakuru by'abanduye, ubukana bw'ubwandu mu baturage, n'ibyago by'abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi (OSHA), kivuga ko akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi ari ugukorana n'abantu ku giti cyabo n'abandi bakozi ku kazi, aho hakoreshwa ingamba zisanzwe zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, kubahiriza imyitwarire myiza mu guhumeka no guhora basukura no guhumeka.
Akazi k'ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi ni akazi katamenyekanye cyangwa kadashidikanywaho ko umuntu afite COVID-19, ariko gasaba guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana n'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Muri abo harimo abakozi bahura n'abaturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari abantu benshi cyane, ndetse no mu maduka acuruza ibintu byinshi.
Usibye ingamba zo kwirinda ubwandu bw'ibanze, ingamba zo kugenzura akaga kuri iri tsinda zirimo gukoresha umwuka uhagije, abarinzi b'imbeho no gushyira ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku bantu mu gihe bahanganye n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi b'ubuzima n'abakora mu bigo by'abicanyi bafite ibyago bikomeye byo guhura n'abantu bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19. Ibyago byongerwa iyo abo bakozi bakoresheje uburyo bwo kuvumbura cyangwa gukusanya ibipimo by'abantu bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Ingamba z'ibyago zikwiye ku bakozi nk'aba harimo ingamba z'ubwubatsi nk'icyumba cy'umwuka utera umwuka mubi, n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye ku kazi.
Iterwa na COVID-19 mu kazi rishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi.
Abakozi bashobora kutabona akazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya guhura n'abandi.
Ubwoko bw'ubucuruzi bushobora guhinduka bitewe n'uburyo ibicuruzwa bihari bikenewe n'uburyo bwo kubikura (urugero, kugura mu gihe nta kazi, cyangwa binyuze mu gutanga cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara ibintu (kugurira mu modoka).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibintu mu turere tuzwiho kuba twatewe cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhungabana. Gahunda yo kwitegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ingamba z'ubwirinzi.
Imigambi yibanda ku nzego zinyuranye z'ibyago bijyanye n'aho bakorera n'akazi bakora, harimo isoko y'ubwandu, ibyago bituruka mu rugo no mu baturage, n'ibyago by'umukozi ku giti cye, nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Basobanuye kandi ingamba zo guhangana n'ibyo byago no kwitegura ibintu bishobora kuvuka biturutse ku cyorezo.
Gahunda zo gutegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura zishobora gukurikiza ibyifuzo by'igihugu cyangwa by'ibihugu.
Mu ntego zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo harimo kugabanya ubwandu mu bakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara zidakwiriye, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo biri mu ikoranabuhanga ryabo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu baturage aho ubucuruzi buri bugira ingaruka ku bisubizo byatanzwe.
Gahunda y'ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago ni umushinga ukoreshwa cyane mu kugenzura umutekano n'ubuzima mu kazi.
Mu gihe ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, ingamba nziza cyane ni iz'ubwubatsi, hanyuma ingamba z'ubuyobozi, hanyuma ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite.
Ingufu z'ubwubatsi zirimo gutandukanya abakozi n'ibyago by'akazi, aho kwishingikiriza ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba umuti uhenze cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Ibihano bya leta ni impinduka mu mabwiriza cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi bisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha agira icyo akora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwa muntu (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora neza cyane kuruta ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda bimwe mu bimenyetso.
Imashini zose z'ubwirinzi zigomba gutoranywa hakurikijwe ibyago by'umukozi, zikagomba kuba zifite ibikwiye (urugero nk'imashini z'ubuhumekero), zidakwiriye kandi zidakwiriye kwambarwa, zigomba kugenzurwa, kuzigirirwa no gusimbuzwa buri gihe, kandi zigomba gufungurwa, gusukurwa no kubikwa neza cyangwa gutakaza kugira ngo zidakora ku bidutanya.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi (OSHA), akazi gashobora gutuma abantu batagirana imishyikirano n'abandi bakozi, mu gihe nta ngaruka nyinshi kagira ku buzima.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu zasabwe ahantu hose hakorerwa imirimo zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi kandi neza, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guha abakozi uburyo bwo guhumeka, harimo no gupfuka mu gihe bakoroye cyangwa batutse, gutanga utwuma n'ibikoresho byo guhanagura imyanda, kwitegura guhanahana amakuru igihe bibaye ngombwa cyangwa gukora amasaha y'akazi, gukangurira abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gahunda yo gusukura no guhanagura imyanda ahantu bakorera.
Kumenya no gushyira mu kato abantu bashobora kwandura vuba ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abasaba akazi n'abandi mu kazi.
Abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, cyatanga inama yo kuguma mu rugo, kugeza igihe bafite umuriro, ibimenyetso by'umuriro, n'ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 badafite imiti igabanya umuriro cyangwa indi miti ihindagurika ibimenyetso, kandi amategeko y'ikiruhuko cyo kurwara agomba koroherezwa, yemerera umukozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo yite ku muntu wo mu muryango urwaye, kandi abakozi bakamenya ayo mategeko.
Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, imirimo y'ibyago byo guhura n'ubwandu iri mu kazi aho COVID-19 itazwi cyangwa ikekwa, ariko hakenewe guhura kenshi cyangwa kwegerana n'abantu bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 mu ntera ya metero esheshatu (1.8 m) bitewe n'indwara ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage mu kazi cyangwa umuntu aherutse gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga mu gace karimo COVID-19 ikwirakwira cyane.
Ibi bisaba abakozi bafatanya n'abantu benshi, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari akaga gakomeye, no mu maduka ahuriranye n'abantu benshi. Ingamba z'ubwubatsi kuri ibi kandi ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi birimo gushyiraho uburyo bwo guhanahana umwuka bwikora neza, kongera umuvuduko w'umwuka, gushyiraho inzitizi z'umubiri nka za plastiki z'isuku, no gushyiraho idirishya ryo gutwara abantu mu kazi, hamwe no gushyiraho uburyo bwo gufasha abakiriya. Ibyo bisaba kandi no ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi, harimo gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo barwaye, guhanahana imbonankubone mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, gutanga amahugurwa ku bakozi bakora mu masaha atandukanye (staggered), gukoresha ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bitagira ingaruka kuri COVID-19, guhanahana n'abakozi mu gihe cy'akazi, guhanagura ibicuruzwa mu buryo bworoshye kandi bworoshye, guhanagura ingendo z'abakozi n'abakozi mu gihe cy'akazi, gushyiraho imipaka, kwigisha abantu uko bakwirinda, kwirinda guhura n'izindi nzitizi, kwirinda COVID-19, kwambara udupfukamunwa n'ibindi bintu byateza akaga, kwirinda guhora mu kazi, kwirinda guhora mu mu mazi, kwirinda ubwandu bw'ibicurane, kwirinda guhura, no kwirinda ibindi bintu bishobora guteza COVID-19.
Abakozi bari muri iri tsinda ry'abashobora guhura n'ibibazo by'uburwayi bakenera gukoresha imashini z'ubuhumekero mu bihe bidasanzwe.
Mu gihe umuntu arwaye mu ndege, ingamba zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bagenzi zirimo gushyira abantu barwaye kure y'abandi metero 6, gushyiraho umuntu wo mu itsinda ry'abakozi wo kwita ku barwayi, no guha abarwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa kubasaba gupfuka umunwa n'amazuru yabo n'utwo mu ruhu igihe batutse cyangwa bakoroye.
Abagenzi bo mu ndege bagomba kwambara uturindantoki tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa igihe bitabye umwungeri urwaye cyangwa bakora ku mazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa ku bintu bishobora kwandura, kandi birashoboka ko bakoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi byiyongereye mu gihe umwungeri urwaye afite umuriro, inkorora idashira cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Inkweto n'ibindi bintu bishobora kujugunywa bigomba kujugunywa mu mufuka w'ibyago by'ibinyabuzima, kandi imiterere yanduye igomba gusukurwa no guhumanywa. Ku mato y'ubucuruzi arimo amato y'imyidagaduro n'andi mato y'abagenzi, ingamba zo kwirinda ibyago harimo gusubika urugendo iyo urwaye, kwigunga no kubwira ikigo nderabuzima cyo ku bwato ako kanya umuntu afite umuriro cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe ari mu bwato.
Mu buryo bwiza, umuntu wahawe akato agomba gukurikiranwa n'abaganga mu cyumba cye. Mu mashuri no mu bigo byita ku bana, CDC irasaba ko niba umuntu wanduye yinjiye mu ishuri, atabanje kureba niba hari ubwandu mu baturage, ryafungwa by'igihe gito kugira ngo ryuhagirwe cyangwa ryice indwara.
Mu gihe hari umubare muto ugereranyije n'uw'abantu benshi bandura, ingamba zo kwirinda abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa, nko guhagarika ingendo zo mu mirima, amakoraniro n'andi materaniro manini, urugero nko kwiga imyuga cyangwa gusangira mu byumba by'ibyokurya cyangwa mu kabari; kongera intera hagati y'amameza, gutandukanya igihe cyo kuza mu biro n'igihe cy'ikiruhuko, kugabanya abantu batajya bahura, no gukoresha ahantu hatandukanye ho gukorera abana bafite ibimenyetso nk'ibicurane.
Iyo indwara yiganje mu baturage, ingamba zo kwirinda abantu bashobora gufata zo kongera igihe cy'ikiruhuko cy'ishuri. Ibikorwa bya buri munsi by'ubugenzacyaha byitwa ko ari ibyago by'ubuzima ku bakora imirimo isanzwe, CDC ivuga ko ari bike.
Abashinzwe kubahiriza amategeko bagomba kuvugana n'abantu bafite COVID-19 yemewe cyangwa bakekwaho, barasabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza nk'ay'abaganga b'ubutabazi bw'ibihe bidasanzwe, harimo ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bukwiriye.
Iyo abakozi bagiranye imishyikirano ya bugufi mu gihe cy'akaga, bagombye gusukura no guhanagura udukingirizo n'ibikoresho byabo bakoresheje isupu cyangwa umwandazi wo mu rugo mbere yo kongera kubikoresha, kandi bagakurikiza uburyo bwo gucunga ibimenyetso bwo kugenzura no gutakaza PPE yakoreshejwe.
OSHA ifata abakozi bamwe na bamwe mu buvuzi n'imfu nk'abafite ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'ibiyobyabwenge.
Akazi gashobora guteza ibyago byinshi harimo abakora mu by'ubuvuzi, abafasha, abakozi bo mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi n'abakora mu by'ingendo z'ubuvuzi, bahura n'abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Iyo abakozi bakora imikorere ituma habaho aérosols, cyangwa bakorakoranya ibipimo cyangwa bagakwirakwiza ibipimo ku barwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ibyo bituma bagira ibyago byinshi byo guhura.
Uburyo bwo gukora aérosol burimo gutera umurindi, uburyo bwo gutangira uburondwe, bronchoscopy, uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo kuvura amenyo no gufata ibipimo binyuze mu gusuzuma cyangwa gukoresha ibikoresho.
Akazi k'ibyago byinshi byo guhura n'urupfu gakubiyemo abakozi bakora mu gutegura imirambo y'abantu bose bari bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kugira COVID-19 igihe bapfaga; biba bishobora gutuma bahura n'ibyago byinshi cyane iyo bakoze autopsies. Ibindi bikorwa by'ubwubatsi byakozwe ku bantu bari mu bantu bafite ibyago byinshi birimo amazu yo kurinda abarwayi bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kugira COVID-19, harimo n'aho bakorera ibikorwa byo gukora aérosols.
Ubwumvikane buke bwihariye bwo guhumeka bushobora kuba bwiza mu bigo bimwe na bimwe by'ubuzima no mu bigo by'ubuvuzi.
Ibipimo bigomba gukoreshwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza yo kwirinda ibifite umutekano muke ku rwego rwa 3.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryasabye ko abarwayi baza bashyirwa mu byumba by'itandukaniro bishingiye ku kuba bakekwaho COVID-19. OSHA itera inkunga ko abantu bafite ibirenge 6 by'abakozi cyangwa abantu bakora imikorere ituma habaho aerosol, hamwe n'abandi bantu bafite SARS-CoV-2 bakekwaho, bakoresha ibikoresho byo guhumeka, uretse ibindi bikoresho bya bwite bikoreshwa mu guhumeka.
Mu gihe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hakorwa igenzura ry'ubuzima, amahugurwa n'ibizamini by'ubuvuzi, hakenewe gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero byemewe na NIOSH N95 cyangwa ibindi bikoreshwa mu guhumeka neza, harimo no gukoresha ibikoresho by'ubuhumekero byemewe na NIOSH.
Ubundi bwoko bw'imashini zo guhumeka zishobora gutanga uburinzi bwinshi kandi zigatuma abakozi barushaho kumererwa neza. OMS ntidushishikariza kwambara umwambaro, kuko COVID-19 idashobora gukwirakwira mu mazi yo mu mubiri, ahubwo ni indwara y'ubuhumekero.
OMS itera inkunga abakozi bakora isuzuma ku marembo gusa kwambara agapfukamunwa.
WHO itera inkunga abantu bakoresha udupfukamunwa, inkofero, cyangwa inkweto zo guhumeka mu gihe bakusanya, kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa kubatwara badafite uburyo bwo gukora ibintu bikurura umwuka.
Niba hari uburyo bwo gukora aerosol, agapfukamunwa ko kubaga gasimbuzwa udupfukamunwa twa N95 cyangwa FFP2.
Kubera ko ku isi hose nta bikoresho bihagije bya PPE bihari, OMS irasaba ko hakoreshwa uburyo bwa telemedicine, intera hagati y'abantu, nk'amadirishya ashyira mu mucyo, kandi abantu bakorana mu buryo butaziguye n'abashinzwe kwita ku barwayi bakinjira mu nzu irimo umurwayi umwe wa COVID-19, bakoresha gusa ibikoresho bya PPE bikenewe mu kazi runaka, bakomeza kubikoresha batirukana imashini z'ubuhumekero mu gihe bita ku barwayi benshi bafite uburwayi bumwe, bakomeza gukurikirana no guhuza uruziga rw'ibikoresho bya PPE, kandi bakemerera abantu badafite ibimenyetso kudakora udupfukamunwa.
