ACE2 itera inzitizi ibikorwa bya enzyme ihindura angiotensin (ACE) ihuje nayo igabanya ingano ya angiotensin-II, kandi ikongera Ang ((1-7) bigatuma iba intego yizewe yo kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora kandi nk'ahantu ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo kuri koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme mu bantu akenshi buvugwa nka hACE2.
Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ni metaloenzym ifite zinc ku mubiri, iba ku gice cy'inyuma cy'umubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite uruziga rwa N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal colectrine urugo rw'umutobe wa amino acide.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bumwe bw'indwara ya membrane ya I, ifite uruhande rw'ingenzi mu bikorwa bya enzymatic ku mibiri y'ibihaha n'indi myenda.
Uruhare rw'inyuma rwa ACE2 rusimburwa n'indi ngirabuzima yitwa shades, ruva mu gice cy'uruhu rw'umubiri, maze poroteyine zishobora gukama zigashyirwa mu maraso, amaherezo zikava mu cyuma.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatanye cyane cyane n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo zifitanye isano na alveoli z'ubwoko bwa II mu bihaha, interocytes zo mu mara mato, ingingo nyinshi z'ingingo z'imitsi n'ingingo z'imitsi n'ingingo z'imitsi n'ingingo z'imitsi n'ingingo z'imitsi.
ACE2 mRNA ivuga kandi mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cortex, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa stratum, mu gice cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cyitwa brainstem.
Inshingano y'ibanze ya ACE2 ni ugukora nk'igihinduranya cya ACE.
ACE igabanyamo ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin I na angiotensin II.
ACE2 itandukanya amino acide ya carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) na angiotensin II maze ikayihindura hydrolyzed mu bwoko bwa angiotensin (1-7) (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora gutandukanya izindi peptides nyinshi, harimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ACE2 itegeka itumanaho ry'urusobe rwa SLC6A19, umushoferi wa amino acide udafite aho uhuriye na yo, kandi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Heartburn.
ACE2 nk'indwara y'uruhu, ikora nk'ahantu h'ingenzi ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituma SARS ifata abantu benshi); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma COVID-19 ifata abantu benshi).
By'umwihariko, SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 bifatanya na poroteyine ya S1 ku gice cy'ingirabuzima cyitwa ACE2 mu gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo, bigatuma habaho endocytosis n'impunzi z'ubwoko bubiri bwa virusi na enzymes mu bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi nzira yo kwinjira ikenera kandi gutangira poroteyine ya S na TMPRSS2 ya serine y'impande, ubu ikorwaho iperereza nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibi byafashije bamwe gutekereza ko kugabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
