b'A urukingo rwa COVID-19 ni urukingo rwiteganyijwe kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo rwarangije igeragezwa mu buvuzi, hari izindi ngamba nyinshi ziri gukorwa mu rwego rwo gukora urwo rukingo.
Mu mpera za Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryavuze ko rititeze ko urukingo rukingira virusi, SARS-CoV-2, ruzabaho mu gihe kitarenze amezi 18.
Muri Mata, hari abakandida batanu b'inkingo bari mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'igeragezwa ry'umutekano.
COVID-19 yagaragaye mu Kuboza 2019.
Mu 2020 habaye icyorezo gikomeye ku isi, bituma habaho ishoramari ryinshi n'ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi mu gukora urukingo.
Ibigo byinshi birimo gukoresha genomes zashyizwe ahagaragara mu gukora inkingo zishoboka zo kurwanya SARS-CoV-2.
Muri Mata, byavuzwe ko icyifuzo cya CEPI cyo gukora urukingo cyari gikeneye umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, ikoreshwa ryinshi no kugera ku isi.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI batangaje ko mu ntangiriro za 2020, ibigo 10 bitandukanye by'ikoranabuhanga byari bikora ubushakashatsi no guteza imbere urukingo rukora neza kuri COVID-19.
Intego nyamukuru z'urubuga zateye imbere mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi ku mutekano zirimo:
Amashami ya nucleic acids (DNA na RNA) (icyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi n'urukingo: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Impamvu zitera virusi (icyiciro cya mbere cy'ubushakashatsi n'urukingo: Cancino Biologica, adenovirus type 5 vector)
Nkuko abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI babivuze muri Mata, abantu 115 bose bakingiwe bari mu byiciro by'ibanze by'iterambere, 78 muri bo bakaba baremejwe nk'imishinga ikora (79 nk'uko byemejwe n'ikigo cya Milken) naho abandi 37 batangazwa nk'abandi, ariko ibyo byose bituruka ku makuru yatanzwe mu ruhame (biteganyijwe ko ateganijwe).
Icyiciro cya I-II cy'igerageza gikora igerageza ry'ibanze ry'umutekano n'ubudahangarwa, kandi akenshi rikorerwa ahantu hatandukanye, hakurikijwe ibipimo bya placebo, mu gihe hashyizweho ibipimo by'ingirakamaro.
Ibizamini bya Phase III birimo kugerageza ubushobozi bw'urukingo mu gukumira indwara n'itsinda ry'ubugenzuzi, akenshi usanga bikubiyemo abenshi mu bitabiriye ibizamini, mu gihe kugenzura ingaruka mbi ku bipimo byiza by'imiti.
"Mu bakandida 79 b'inkingo bari mu iterambere rikomeye (nk'uko byemejwe mu ntangiriro za Mata 2020), 74 ntibari barigeze basuzumwa ku bantu (bwari mu bushakashatsi bwo mu rwego rwa 'preclinical')".
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020, Kaminuza ya Queensland muri Ositaraliya yatangaje ko irimo gukora ubushakashatsi ku bushobozi bw'urukingo rufite ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'indwara, rushobora guhindura za poroteyine za virusi mu buryo bw'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo kugira ngo zitume habaho ibisubizo by'ubudahangarwa.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 muri Canada, Ikigo Mpuzamahanga cy'Incanco cya Kaminuza ya Saskatchewan (VIDO-Intervac) cyatangaje ko gitangiye gukora ku rukingo rugamije gutangira igerageza ku bantu mu 2021.
Imishinga yo guteza imbere inkingo yatangajwe ku ya 26 Mutarama 2020 muri Chinese Center for Disease Control and Prevention na Kaminuza ya Hong Kong ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
