Ku ya 25 Werurwe, umuyobozi w'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi yatangaje ko basoje ikorwa ry'urukingo kandi ko batangiye kugerageza.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare 2020, Newgenerex Immuno-Oncology, isosiyete ikorana na Generax, yatangaje ko iri gutangiza umushinga w'urukingo rwo gukora urukingo rwa peptide ya LI-Kirwanya COVID-19.
Bashakaga gukora urukingo rushobora kugeragezwa ku bantu mu minsi 90.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis yatangaje ko ifite gahunda yo gukora urukingo.
