Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ubuzima y'u Buhinde yatangaje ko ikora ku bisasu 11 byigenga kandi ko nubwo biri mu muvuduko wo kwihuta, bizatwara nibura imyaka 1.5 kugeza kuri 2 kugira ngo haboneke urukingo.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga mu by'ibinyabuzima muri Québec City, muri Québec, cyavuze ko cyavumbuye imiterere ya virusi ya corona, ifashijwe n'ikigo cya Canada gishinzwe ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuzima (Canadian Institutes for Health Research).
