Mu ntangiriro z'iki cyumweru, ikinyamakuru The Guardian cyatangaje ko Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Donald Trump yasabye Kourivak "amafaranga menshi" kugira ngo igire umwihariko ku rukingo rwa Covid-19, Leta y'u Budage ikaba yarayamaganiye kure.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe 2020, ikigo cy'imiti cy'Abanyamerika Pfizer cyatangaje ko kizakorana n'ikigo cy'Abadage BioNTech mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo rushingiye kuri mRNA.
