Ku ya 17 Werurwe 2020 mu Butaliyani, ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cy'Ubutaliyani cyitwa Takis Biotech cyatangaje ko kizaba gifite ibisubizo by'igeragezwa rya mbere y'igeragezwa muri Mata 2020, kandi ko umukandida wabo wa nyuma w'urukingo ashobora kugeragezwa ku bantu mu itumba.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, Coalition for Epidemic Preparedness Innovations (CEPI) mu Bufaransa yatangaje ko izashora miliyoni 4.9 z'amadolari ya Amerika mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku rukingo rwa COVID-19, kizaba kirimo Institut Pasteur, Themis Bioscience (Vienne, Austria) na Kaminuza ya Pittsburgh, bifata ishoramari rusange rya CEPI mu gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 rikaba rigera kuri miliyoni 29 z'amadolari ya Amerika.
Abandi bashoramari ba CEPI mu gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 ni Moderna, Curevac, Inovio, Novavax, Kaminuza ya Hong Kong, Kaminuza ya Oxford na Kaminuza ya Queensland.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe 2020, abayobozi b'ubuzima mu Burusiya batangaje ko abahanga batangiye kugerageza inkingo esheshatu zitandukanye ku nyamaswa.
Abashakashatsi bo muri Imperial College London batangaje ku ya 20 Werurwe 2020 ko barimo gukora urukingo rwa RNA rwigenga kuri COVID-19.
