Mu mpera za Werurwe, Guverinoma ya Kanada yatangaje inkunga ya C$275 miliyoni ku mishinga 96 y'ubushakashatsi ku kurwanya COVID-19, irimo n'imishinga y'ibigo na kaminuza nyinshi zo muri Kanada, nk'iya MedicaGo na Saskatchewan.
"Igihe kimwe, Guverinoma ya Kanada yatangaje inkunga ya C$192 miliyoni mu buryo bwihariye yo gukora inkingo za COVID-19, ndetse n'izindi nkingo nshya zitari nke, ndetse n'umugambi wo gushyiraho "banki y'inkingo" ku rwego rw'igihugu, zishobora gukoreshwa mu gihe hazabaho ikindi cyorezo cya coronavirus".
"Ku ya 2 Mata 2020, abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Pittsburgh School of Medicine batangaje ku igeragezwa ry'urukingo rwa COVID-19 rushobora gukoreshwa ku ngurube, rwitwa PittCoVacc, bavuga ko ""inkingo za SARS-CoV-2 S1 z'urwego ruto zashyizweho na MNA zagize ibisubizo bikomeye bya antigen-specific antibody [mu ngurube] bigaragara mu cyumweru cya 2 nyuma yo gukingirwa"."
Ku ya 16 Mata 2020 muri Canada, Kaminuza ya Waterloo Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi ryatangaje gahunda yo gukora urukingo rushingiye kuri ADN nk'ikinyugunyugu cy'umuhogo.
ADN izashushanywa ikoresheje bacteriophage kugira ngo ishobore kwigana muri bagiteri z'abantu, kugira ngo haboneke ingirabuzimafatizo zimeze nk'ubwandu bw'agakoko nta cyo butwaye, zishobora gutuma abasirikare b'umubiri bakora za 'antibodies' zihangana na SARS-CoV-2.
Muri Werurwe 2020, guverinoma ya Amerika, inganda na kaminuza eshatu, bigizwe na Hewlett Packard Enterprise, Amazon, Microsoft na Google, ikoranabuhanga rya cloud computing, byashyizeho uburyo bwo kugera kuri mudasobwa nini za IBM.
Hariho impinduka zimwe na zimwe zifite ingaruka za heterolagus, zizwi kandi nk'ingaruka zidafite umwihariko.
Ibi bivuze ko hari ibyiza bishobora kuboneka birenze ibyo kwirinda indwara.
