Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze mu gusuzuma imikorere y'inkingo mu nyamaswa zihariye za COVID-19, nk'imbeba za ACE2-transgenic, izindi nyamaswa zo mu ma laboratoire n'inyamaswa zitari abantu, bugaragaza ko hakenewe ibipimo bya biosefete-level 3 byo kugenzura no guhuza mpuzamahanga mu gucunga virusi nzima kugira ngo haboneke uburyo bwo kurinda bufite ireme.
Inkingo za SARS na MERS zagejejwe mu igeragezwa ku nyamaswa zitari abantu.
Muri 2020, nta muti cyangwa urukingo rw'ubwirinzi kuri SARS rwigaragaje ko rufite umutekano kandi rukora neza ku bantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu nyandiko z'ubushakashatsi zasohotse mu 2005 na 2006, gutahura no guteza imbere inkingo n'imiti mishya yo kuvura SARS byari ibintu by'ingenzi cyane ku butegetsi n'ibigo by'ubuzima rusange ku isi.
Igihe MERS yadukaga, byemezwaga ko ubushakashatsi kuri SARS bwariho bushobora gutanga icyitegererezo cyiza cyo gukora inkingo n'inkingo zo kurwanya ubwandu bwa MERS-CoV.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari urukingo rwa MERS (rushingiye kuri ADN) rwasoje igeragezwa rya mbere mu bantu, kandi hari izindi eshatu zikomeje, zose ni urukingo rw'indwara ziterwa na virusi, ebyiri ziterwa na adénoviral (ChAdOx1-MERS, BVRS-GamVac) na imwe iterwa na MVA (MVA-MERS-S).
Inyandiko zo ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zakwirakwije ibitekerezo by'ubuhendanyi bivuga ko virusi ituma COVID-19 iba izwi kandi ko urukingo rwamaze kuboneka.
Impushya zo mu rwego rw'amategeko zivugwa mu nyandiko zitandukanye ku mbuga nkoranyambaga zifitanye isano n'impushya zihari ku miterere y'imiterere y'ingirabuzima fatizo n'inkingo z'ubundi bwoko bwa coronavirus, nk'iyo SARS.
B'Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara yanduza iterwa n'indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye cyane yitwa Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo umuriro, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibindi bimenyetso bishobora kuba harimo umunaniro, ububabare bw'umubiri, iseseme, kubabara mu muhogo, kutabona neza impumuro no kubabara mu nda.
Igihe cyo kuva ku muntu wahuye na virusi kugeza ku kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ubusanzwe ni iminsi itanu, ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza kuri 14.
Nubwo akenshi hari ibimenyetso byoroheje, hari igihe bishobora gutera indwara y'ibicurane n'imyanya myinshi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Mata 2020, hari hamaze kuboneka abarwayi barenga miliyoni 2.24 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bihitana abantu barenga 153.000.
Abantu barenga 568,000 bakize. Virusi ibanza gukwirakwira mu bantu binyuze mu tuntu duto tw'amacandwe dukunze guterwa no gukorora, kwitsamura cyangwa kuvuga mu gihe cy'imibonano ya bugufi.
Iyo uduhumeke tw'amacandwe dukomoka mu mwuka, akenshi tugwa hasi cyangwa ku butaka aho kuba ahantu harehare.
Abantu bashobora kwandura bakimara gukora ku bintu byanduye, bakoresheje amaso, amazuru cyangwa umunwa.
Virusi ishobora kubaho ku mibiri y'abantu mu gihe cy'amasaha 72.
Ni indwara yandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere y'igiteranyo cy'indwara, nubwo ishobora kwandura mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara no mu bindi byiciro by'indwara. Uburyo bwiza bwo gupima ni uburyo bwo gusuzuma mu gihe cy'igihe cy'igihe cy'imikorere y'indwara ya polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) mu buryo bw'imikorere y'indwara ya nasopharyngeal swab.
Abantu bakekwaho kwandura iyi virus n'ababafasha basabwa kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Ibitekerezo ku gukoresha udupfukamunwa ku baturage muri rusange biratandukanye, hari abategetsi batugira inama yo kutadukoresha, hari abatugira inama yo kudukoresha, n'abandi badusaba ko tubikoresha.
Kugeza ubu nta rukingo cyangwa imiti yihariye ya COVID-19 igaragaza ko ishobora kurwanya virusi.
Mu bihugu byinshi byo mu turere dutandatu twa WHO, hari abantu bandura iyi ndwara mu karere.
Abantu banduye virusi bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso cyangwa bakagira ibimenyetso bisa n'iby'ibicurane, urugero nk'umuriro, inkorora, umunaniro no guhumeka nabi.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi birimo guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu gatuza cyangwa gukomera, urujijo, kugorwa no kubyuka no kugira ubururu mu maso cyangwa ku munwa; iyo ibi bimenyetso bihari, kwihutira gushaka ubuvuzi birahanwa.
Ibimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara cyane, birimo no guhumeka hejuru, nko kwitsamura, gusohora amazi mu mazuru cyangwa kubabara mu muhogo.
Ibimenyetso byo mu maraso n'impyiko nk'umunaniro, gusubiranamo no kuribwa cyane byerekanwe mu bice bitandukanye.
Mu Bushinwa, hari abanduye bagaragaye bafite ibihaha bihinda kandi bihinda.
Mu bantu bamwe, iyi ndwara ishobora gutera amapfa, guhagarika imyanya myinshi y'umubiri ndetse no gupfa.
Ni cyo bita igihe cyo gukura kwa mikorobe.
Icyiciro cy'uburumbuke bwa COVID-19 gisanzwe kimara iminsi itanu cyangwa itandatu ariko gishobora kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi 14.
Abantu 97.5% bagaragaza ibimenyetso mu minsi 11.5 nyuma yo kwandura. Raporo zigaragaza ko abanduye bose batagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Uruhare rw'abo batwara indwara badafite ibimenyetso mu kwanduzanya ntiruzwi neza; ariko ibimenyetso bya mbere bigaragaza ko bashobora kugira uruhare mu gukwirakwiza iyi ndwara.
Umubare w'abanduye batagaragaza ibimenyetso muri iki gihe ntiwamenyekanye kandi urimo kwigwa, raporo y'ikigo cyo muri Koreya cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (KCDC) ivuga ko 20% by'abanduye bose bemejwe batagaragaza ibimenyetso mu gihe bari mu bitaro.
Ku ya 1 Mata, Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa yatangiye gushyira mu mubare w'abarwayi batagira ibimenyetso mu bipimo byayo bya buri munsi; abantu 130 (78%) mu 166 banduye uwo munsi ntibagiraga ibimenyetso.
Amata n'amahembe byombi bishobora gutwara virusi nyinshi.
Iyo uvuga cyane kurusha uko uvugira bisanzwe, usohora udusabo twinshi tw'amacandwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe muri Singapore bwagaragaje ko gukorora udatwikiriye mu maso bishobora gutuma udutotsi duto tw'amaraso twigaragaza ku metero 4.5 (15 ft).
Nubwo virusi idakunze kwanduzwa n'umwuka, Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubumenyi cyerekanye ko kwandura bioaerosol bishoboka kandi ko ingufu z'umwuka zifungiwe mu nzira z'inzu z'abantu zatanze ibipimo byiza bya RNA ya virusi.
Uburyo bumwe na bumwe bwo kuvura, nko guterwa intanga n'umutima (CPR), bushobora gutuma umwanda wo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero uhinduka uduce two mu kirere, bigatuma habaho gukwirakwira mu kirere.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora gukwirakwira mu binyamubiri, iki cyorezo gifatwa nk'aho ari gito. Virusi yibasira cyane iyo abantu bagaragaje ibimenyetso; birashoboka ko ikwirakwira mbere yuko ibimenyetso bigaragara ariko ibyago ni bike.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko bitamenyekanye neza uko iyi ndwara yandura mu buryo bworoshye, ariko ko umuntu umwe ubusanzwe yandura abantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
By'umwihariko, virusi yasanzwe ishobora kugaragara ku ikarito mu gihe cy'umunsi umwe, mu plastiki (polypropylene) no mu cyuma kidafite ingeso (AISI 304) mu gihe cy'iminsi itatu, no mu cyuma cya 99% mu gihe cy'amasaha ane.
Ibi biterwa n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe.
Amasabune na detergents nabyo birashobora kugira akamaro iyo bikoreshejwe neza; ibicuruzwa by'amasabune bisenya uruziga rw'ibinure bya virusi, bikabihagarika kandi bikabirekura ku ruhu no ku yindi mibiri.
Ibindi bisubizo, nka benzalkonium chloride na chlorhexidine gluconate (ubuvuzi bw'imiti yica udukoko) ntibikora neza. Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Hong Kong, ibipimo by'amaraso byafashwe hagati y'iminsi ibiri nyuma yo kwinjira mu bitaro.
Ibipimo bya mbere byafashwe ku murwayi wa gatanu muri batandatu byagaragaje ko afite virusi nyinshi, naho ku wa gatandatu, byafashwe ku munsi wa kabiri, byagaragaje ko afite virusi nyinshi.
Indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni coronavirus nshya y'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero, yabanje gutandukanywa n'abantu batatu barwaye ibicurane by'ibicurane by'ibicurane by'ubuhumekero i Wuhan.
Imiterere yose ya virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 igaragara mu bwoko bwa koronavirusi.
Hasi y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yica isabune yo mu rugo, ikamenagura ibibyimba byayo birinda. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV y'inkomoko.
Ibihaha ni byo bice byugarijwe cyane na COVID-19 kuko virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo binyuze muri enzymes izwi nka angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2), iboneka cyane mu ngirabuzimafatizo za alveolar z'ubwoko bwa II mu bihaha.
"Kugira ngo virusi ifatanye na ACE2 kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, ikoresha poroteyine yihariye yo ku buringanire bw'umubiri yitwa ""spike"" (peplomeres)".
Ibibazo by'imvune ikomeye y'umutima byagaragariye mu bantu 12% banduye bari mu bitaro byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, kandi birushaho kwiyongera mu barwayi bakomeye.
Ibipimo by'indwara z'umutima n'amaraso biri hejuru kubera ibisubizo by'ubuhumekero n'ubuhumekero mu gihe cy'irema ry'indwara, ariko ibikomere bikomeye by'umutima bishobora no kuba bifitanye isano n'ibinure bya ACE2 by'umutima.
ACE2 ibyara vuba mu mutima kandi igira uruhare mu mikorere y'umutima.
Indwara ya COVID-19 yagaragaye mu barwayi bo muri ICU bafite indwara ya thrombosis (31%) na thromboembolicisme ya vena (25%) kandi ishobora kuba ifitanye isano n'uburwayi. Iraporo z'abantu bapfuye bazize COVID-19 zagaragaje ubwandu bw'amahembe (diffuse alveolar damage, DAD), n'udutsi tw'indwara tw'amahembe tw'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
Nubwo SARS-COV-2 ikunda kwerekeza ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'urwagashya zihurira mu nzira y'ubuhumekero - ACE2, abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye cyane bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'ubushyuhe bukabije.
By'umwihariko, mu barwayi ba COVID-19 hagaragaye ko ingirabuzimafatizo za T zitanga GM-CSF zifite ubukana zifitanye isano n'imibonano mpuzabitsina itangiza IL-6 n'indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha.
Ibizamini by'umurambo byagaragaje ko hari udukoko twitwa lymphocyte twinjiye mu mubiri.
OMS yashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza y'igerageza ry'iki cyorezo.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo gupima bukoresha uburyo bwo gupima bwa Real-Time Reverse Transcription Polymerase Chain Reaction (rRT-PCR).
Ikigeragezo gikunze gukorerwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe na swab ya nosopharyngeal; ariko, swab ya nasal cyangwa ibipimo by'amacandwe nabyo birashobora gukoreshwa.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Ibizamini by'amaraso birashoboka, ariko bisaba gufata ibipimo bibiri by'amaraso mu byumweru bibiri kandi ibisubizo bifite agaciro gake.
Abahanga mu bya siyansi b'Abashinwa bashoboye gutandukanya ubwoko bwa coronavirus no gusohora urutonde rwayo rw'ibinyabuzima kugira ngo laboratwari ku isi hose zishobore gukora ibizamini bya polymerase chain reaction (PCR) ku giti cyazo kugira ngo zimenye ubwandu bw'iyi virusi.
